320102,82,629,2,4,1,18,2,9 . Āghātavatthusuttaṃ 
320103,82,630,2,22,1,35,3,"79.[ a. ni.9.29]‘‘ Dasayimāni, bhikkhave, āghātavatthūni. "
320104,82,630,23,25,1,13,2,Katamāni dasa?
320105,82,630,26,34,1,37,6,‘ Anatthaṃ me acarī’ ti āghātaṃ bandhati;
320106,82,630,35,43,1,38,6,‘ anatthaṃ me caratī’ ti āghātaṃ bandhati;
320107,82,630,44,52,1,41,6,‘ anatthaṃ me carissatī’ ti āghātaṃ bandhati;
320108,82,630,53,107,1,202,32,"‘ piyassa me manāpassa anatthaṃ acarī’ ti… pe…‘ anatthaṃ caratī’ ti… pe…‘ anatthaṃ carissatī’ ti āghātaṃ bandhati,‘ appiyassa me amanāpassa atthaṃ acarī’ ti… pe…‘ atthaṃ caratī’ ti… pe…‘ atthaṃ carissatī’ ti āghātaṃ bandhati; "
320109,82,630,108,122,1,61,9,"aṭṭhāne ca kuppati– imāni kho, bhikkhave, dasa āghātavatthūnī’’ ti. "
320110,82,630,123,124,1,7,1,Navamaṃ.
320111,82,631,2,4,1,22,2,10 . Āghātapaṭivinayasuttaṃ 
320112,82,632,2,14,1,35,3,"80.‘‘ Dasayime , bhikkhave, āghātapaṭivinayā. "
320113,82,632,15,17,1,11,2,Katame dasa?
320114,82,632,18,116,1,464,67,"‘ Anatthaṃ me acari, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti ,‘ anatthaṃ me carati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti,‘ anatthaṃ me carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhā’ ti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, piyassa me manāpassa anatthaṃ acari… pe… carati… pe… carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṃ paṭivineti , appiyassa me amanāpassa atthaṃ acari… pe… atthaṃ carati… pe… atthaṃ carissati, taṃ kutettha labbhāti āghātaṃ paṭivineti, aṭṭhāne ca na kuppati– ime kho, bhikkhave, dasa āghātapaṭivinayā’’ ti. "
