320120,82,637,1,7,1,10,1,(9)4. Theravaggo
320121,82,638,2,4,1,12,2,1 . Vāhanasuttaṃ 
320122,82,639,2,15,1,66,8,81. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā campāyaṃ viharati gaggarāya pokkharaṇiyā tīre. 
320123,82,639,16,23,1,49,7,Atha kho āyasmā vāhano yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
320124,82,639,24,29,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
320125,82,639,30,37,1,57,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā vāhano bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
320126,82,639,38,58,1,105,13,"‘‘ katihi nu kho, bhante, dhammehi tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharatī’’ ti?"
320127,82,640,2,18,1,99,12,"‘ ‘ Dasahi kho, vāhana, dhammehi tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharati. "
320128,82,640,19,21,1,15,2,Katamehi dasahi? 
320129,82,640,22,90,1,344,45,"Rūpena kho, vāhana, tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharati, vedanāya kho, vāhana… pe… saññāya kho, vāhana… saṅkhārehi kho, vāhana… viññāṇena kho, vāhana… jātiyā kho, vāhana… jarāya kho, vāhana… maraṇena kho, vāhana… dukkhehi kho, vāhana… kilesehi kho, vāhana, tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharati. "
320130,82,640,91,110,1,127,17,"Seyyathāpi, vāhana, uppalaṃ vā padumaṃ vā puṇḍarīkaṃ vā udake jātaṃ udake saṃvaḍḍhaṃ udakā paccuggamma ṭhitaṃ anupalittaṃ udakena; "
320131,82,640,111,129,1,117,14,"evamevaṃ kho, vāhana, imehi dasahi dhammehi tathāgato nissaṭo visaṃyutto vippamutto vimariyādīkatena cetasā viharatī’’ ti. "
320132,82,640,130,131,1,8,1,Paṭhamaṃ.
320133,82,641,2,4,1,12,2,2 . Ānandasuttaṃ 
320134,82,642,2,13,1,49,7,82. Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
320135,82,642,14,19,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
320136,82,642,20,27,1,59,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ bhagavā etadavoca–
320137,82,643,2,23,1,119,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ assaddho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320138,82,644,2,22,1,118,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ dussīlo samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320139,82,645,2,22,1,120,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ appassuto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320140,82,646,2,24,1,118,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ dubbaco samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320141,82,647,2,22,1,120,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ pāpamitto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320142,82,648,2,22,1,117,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ kusīto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320143,82,649,2,22,1,122,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ muṭṭhassati samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320144,82,650,2,23,1,121,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ asantuṭṭho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320145,82,651,2,22,1,119,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ pāpiccho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320146,82,652,2,23,1,125,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ micchādiṭṭhiko samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320147,82,653,2,24,1,137,18,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ imehi dasahi dhammehi samannāgato imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti netaṃ ṭhānaṃ vijjati."
320148,82,654,2,21,1,115,15,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ saddho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
320149,82,655,2,21,1,115,15,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ sīlavā samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
320150,82,656,2,22,1,128,16,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ bahussuto sutadharo samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
320151,82,657,2,21,1,115,15,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ suvaco samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
320152,82,658,2,22,1,121,15,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ kalyāṇamitto samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
320153,82,659,2,21,1,122,15,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ āraddhavīriyo samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
320154,82,660,2,22,1,123,15,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ upaṭṭhitassati samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
320155,82,661,2,22,1,118,15,"‘ ‘ So vatānanda, bhikkhu‘ santuṭṭho samāno imasmiṃ dhammavinaye vuddhiṃ virūḷhiṃ vepullaṃ āpajjissatī’ ti ṭhānametaṃ vijjati."
