320216,82,686,2,4,1,12,2,5 . Katthīsuttaṃ 
320217,82,687,2,13,1,57,7,85. Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā mahācundo cetīsu viharati sahajātiyaṃ. 
320218,82,687,14,20,1,43,6,Tatra kho āyasmā mahācundo bhikkhū āmantesi–
