320429,82,766,2,4,1,14,2,8 . Akkosakasuttaṃ 
320430,82,767,2,52,1,148,16,"88.‘‘ Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akkosakaparibhāsako ariyūpavādī sabrahmacārīnaṃ ṭhānametaṃ avakāso[ aṭṭhānametaṃ anavakāso( sī. syā. pī.)] yaṃ so dasannaṃ byasanānaṃ aññataraṃ byasanaṃ nigaccheyya[ na nigaccheyya( sī. syā. pī.)]. "
320431,82,767,53,55,1,18,2,Katamesaṃ dasannaṃ? 
320432,82,767,56,104,1,336,40,"Anadhigataṃ nādhigacchati, adhigatā parihāyati, saddhammassa na vodāyanti, saddhammesu vā adhimāniko hoti anabhirato vā brahmacariyaṃ carati, aññataraṃ vā saṃkiliṭṭhaṃ āpattiṃ āpajjati, gāḷhaṃ vā rogātaṅkaṃ phusati, ummādaṃ vā pāpuṇāti cittakkhepaṃ, sammūḷho kālaṃ karoti, kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati. "
320433,82,767,105,128,1,158,18,"Yo so, bhikkhave, bhikkhu akkosakaparibhāsako ariyūpavādī sabrahmacārīnaṃ, ṭhānametaṃ avakāso yaṃ so imesaṃ dasannaṃ byasanānaṃ aññataraṃ byasanaṃ nigaccheyyā’’ ti. "
320434,82,767,129,130,1,8,1,Aṭṭhamaṃ.
320435,82,768,2,4,1,14,2,9 . Kokālikasuttaṃ 
320436,82,769,2,29,1,52,7,89.[ saṃ. ni.1.181; su. ni. kokālikasutta] Atha kho kokāliko bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
320437,82,769,30,35,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
320438,82,769,36,43,1,60,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho kokāliko bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
320439,82,769,44,59,1,68,8,"‘‘ pāpicchā, bhante, sāriputtamoggallānā, pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gatā’’ ti."
320440,82,769,60,72,1,35,6,"‘‘ Mā hevaṃ, kokālika, mā hevaṃ, kokālika! "
320441,82,769,73,79,1,46,4,"Pasādehi, kokālika, sāriputtamoggallānesu cittaṃ. "
320442,82,769,80,85,1,29,3,Pesalā sāriputtamoggallānā’’ ti. 
320443,82,770,2,8,1,52,6,Dutiyampi kho kokāliko bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
320444,82,770,9,32,1,119,15,"‘‘ kiñcāpi me, bhante, bhagavā saddhāyiko paccayiko, atha kho pāpicchāva sāriputtamoggallānā, pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gatā’’ ti."
320445,82,770,33,44,1,35,6,"‘‘ Mā hevaṃ, kokālika, mā hevaṃ, kokālika! "
320446,82,770,45,52,1,46,4,"Pasādehi, kokālika, sāriputtamoggallānesu cittaṃ. "
320447,82,770,53,58,1,29,3,Pesalā sāriputtamoggallānā’’ ti. 
320448,82,771,2,8,1,52,6,Tatiyampi kho kokāliko bhikkhu bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
320449,82,771,9,32,1,119,15,"‘‘ kiñcāpi me, bhante, bhagavā saddhāyiko paccayiko, atha kho pāpicchāva sāriputtamoggallānā, pāpikānaṃ icchānaṃ vasaṃ gatā’’ ti."
320450,82,771,33,44,1,35,6,"‘‘ Mā hevaṃ, kokālika, mā hevaṃ, kokālika! "
320451,82,771,45,52,1,46,4,"Pasādehi, kokālika , sāriputtamoggallānesu cittaṃ. "
320452,82,771,53,58,1,29,3,Pesalā sāriputtamoggallānā’’ ti. 
320453,82,772,2,12,1,87,10,Atha kho kokāliko bhikkhu uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. 
320454,82,772,13,23,1,87,10,Acirapakkantassa ca kokālikassa bhikkhuno sāsapamattīhi pīḷakāhi sabbo kāyo phuṭo ahosi. 
320455,82,772,24,91,1,363,34,"Sāsapamattiyo hutvā muggamattiyo ahesuṃ, muggamattiyo hutvā kalāyamattiyo ahesuṃ, kalāyamattiyo hutvā kolaṭṭhimattiyo ahesuṃ, kolaṭṭhimattiyo hutvā kolamattiyo ahesuṃ, kolamattiyo hutvā āmalakamattiyo ahesuṃ, āmalakamattiyo hutvā( tiṇḍukamattiyo ahesuṃ, tiṇḍukamattiyo hutvā,)[ saṃ. ni.1.181; su. ni. kokālikasutta natthi] beḷuvasalāṭukamattiyo ahesuṃ, beḷuvasalāṭukamattiyo hutvā billamattiyo ahesuṃ, billamattiyo hutvā pabhijjiṃsu, pubbañca lohitañca pagghariṃsu. "
320456,82,772,92,98,1,47,6,So sudaṃ kadalipattesu seti macchova visagilito. 
320457,82,773,2,40,1,63,8,"Atha kho turū paccekabrahmā[ tuduppaccekabrahmā( sī. pī.), tudi paccekabrahmā( syā.), turi paccekabrahmā( ka.) saṃ. ni.1.180] yena kokāliko bhikkhu tenupasaṅkami; "
320458,82,773,41,47,1,56,6,upasaṅkamitvā vehāse ṭhatvā kokālikaṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca–
320459,82,773,48,56,1,46,4,"‘‘ pasādehi, kokālika, sāriputtamoggallānesu cittaṃ. "
320460,82,773,57,62,1,29,3,Pesalā sāriputtamoggallānā’’ ti.
320461,82,773,63,72,1,18,4,"‘‘ Kosi tvaṃ, āvuso’’ ti?"
320462,82,773,73,81,1,26,4,‘‘ Ahaṃ turū paccekabrahmā’’ ti.
320463,82,773,82,96,1,65,9,"‘‘ Nanu tvaṃ, āvuso, bhagavatā anāgāmī byākato, atha kiñcarahi idhāgato? "
320464,82,773,97,105,1,35,6,Passa yāvañca te idaṃ aparaddhan’’ ti. 
320465,82,774,2,12,1,65,8,Atha kho turū paccekabrahmā kokālikaṃ bhikkhuṃ gāthāhi ajjhabhāsi–
320466,82,775,2,11,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Purisassa hi jātassa, kuṭhārī jāyate mukhe; "
320467,82,776,2,9,1,45,6,"Yāya chindati attānaṃ, bālo dubbhāsitaṃ bhaṇaṃ."
320468,82,777,2,13,1,49,9,"‘ ‘ Yo nindiyaṃ pasaṃsati, taṃ vā nindati yo pasaṃsiyo; "
320469,82,778,2,12,1,55,9,"Vicināti mukhena so kaliṃ, kalinā tena sukhaṃ na vindati."
320470,82,779,2,11,1,46,7,"‘ ‘ Appamattako ayaṃ kali, yo akkhesu dhanaparājayo; "
320471,82,780,2,9,1,47,6,"Sabbassāpi sahāpi attanā, ayameva mahattaro kali; "
320472,82,781,2,6,1,26,4,Yo sugatesu manaṃ padūsaye.
320473,82,782,2,13,1,59,8,"‘ ‘ Sataṃ sahassānaṃ nirabbudānaṃ, chattiṃsati pañca ca abbudāni; "
320474,82,783,2,13,1,63,8,"Yamariyagarahī nirayaṃ upeti, vācaṃ manañca paṇidhāya pāpakan’’ ti. "
320475,82,784,2,10,1,52,7,Atha kho kokāliko bhikkhu teneva ābādhena kālamakāsi. 
320476,82,784,11,21,1,95,10,Kālaṅkato ca kokāliko bhikkhu padumaṃ nirayaṃ upapajjati sāriputtamoggallānesu cittaṃ āghātetvā. 
