320561,82,813,17,27,1,66,8,"Idha, gahapati, ekacco kāmabhogī adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasena; "
320562,82,813,28,57,1,99,14,adhammena bhoge pariyesitvā sāhasena na attānaṃ sukheti na pīṇeti[ na attānaṃ sukheti pīṇeti( sī. syā. pī.) evamuparipi] na saṃvibhajati na puññāni karoti.
320563,82,814,2,16,1,71,10,"‘ ‘ Idha pana, gahapati, ekacco kāmabhogī adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasena; "
320564,82,814,17,30,1,93,12,"adhammena bhoge pariyesitvā sāhasena attānaṃ sukheti pīṇeti, na saṃvibhajati na puññāni karoti."
320565,82,815,2,16,1,71,10,"‘ ‘ Idha pana , gahapati, ekacco kāmabhogī adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasena; "
320566,82,815,17,27,1,87,10,adhammena bhoge pariyesitvā sāhasena attānaṃ sukheti pīṇeti saṃvibhajati puññāni karoti.
