320579,82,821,27,69,1,85,9,Te ca bhoge gathito[ gadhito( ka.) a. ni.3.124 passitabbaṃ] mucchito ajjhosanno[ ajjhāpanno( sabbattha) a. ni.3.124 suttavaṇṇanā ṭīkā oloketabbā] anādīnavadassāvī anissaraṇapañño paribhuñjati.
320580,82,822,2,15,1,71,10,"‘ ‘ Idha pana, gahapati, ekacco kāmabhogī dhammena bhoge pariyesati asāhasena; "
320581,82,822,16,26,1,87,10,dhammena bhoge pariyesitvā asāhasena attānaṃ sukheti pīṇeti saṃvibhajati puññāni karoti. 
320582,82,822,27,36,1,86,9,Te ca bhoge agathito amucchito anajjhosanno ādīnavadassāvī nissaraṇapañño paribhuñjati.
320583,82,823,2,38,1,212,29,"‘ ‘ Tatra, gahapati, yvāyaṃ kāmabhogī adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasena, adhammena bhoge pariyesitvā sāhasena na attānaṃ sukheti na pīṇeti na saṃvibhajati na puññāni karoti, ayaṃ, gahapati, kāmabhogī tīhi ṭhānehi gārayho."
320584,82,823,39,51,1,70,9,"‘ Adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasenā’ ti, iminā paṭhamena ṭhānena gārayho."
320585,82,823,52,66,1,62,10,"‘ Na attānaṃ sukheti na pīṇetī’ ti, iminā dutiyena ṭhānena gārayho."
320586,82,823,67,80,1,67,10,"‘ Na saṃvibhajati na puññāni karotī’ ti, iminā tatiyena ṭhānena gārayho. "
320587,82,823,81,90,1,50,7,"Ayaṃ, gahapati, kāmabhogī imehi tīhi ṭhānehi gārayho."
320588,82,824,2,39,1,229,30,"‘ ‘ Tatra, gahapati, yvāyaṃ kāmabhogī adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasena, adhammena bhoge pariyesitvā sāhasena attānaṃ sukheti pīṇeti na saṃvibhajati na puññāni karoti, ayaṃ, gahapati, kāmabhogī dvīhi ṭhānehi gārayho ekena ṭhānena pāsaṃso."
320589,82,824,40,52,1,70,9,"‘ Adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasenā’ ti, iminā paṭhamena ṭhānena gārayho."
320590,82,824,53,64,1,53,8,"‘ Attānaṃ sukheti pīṇetī’ ti, iminā ekena ṭhānena pāsaṃso."
320591,82,824,65,77,1,67,10,‘ Na saṃvibhajati na puññāni karotī’ ti iminā dutiyena ṭhānena gārayho. 
320592,82,824,78,91,1,79,11,"Ayaṃ, gahapati, kāmabhogī imehi dvīhi ṭhānehi gārayho iminā ekena ṭhānena pāsaṃso."
320593,82,825,2,39,1,223,28,"‘ ‘ Tatra , gahapati, yvāyaṃ kāmabhogī adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasena , adhammena bhoge pariyesitvā sāhasena attānaṃ sukheti pīṇeti saṃvibhajati puññāni karoti, ayaṃ, gahapati, kāmabhogī ekena ṭhānena gārayho dvīhi ṭhānehi pāsaṃso."
320594,82,825,40,52,1,66,9,"‘ Adhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasenā’ ti, iminā ekena ṭhānena gārayho."
320595,82,825,53,65,1,57,8,"‘ Attānaṃ sukheti pīṇetī’ ti, iminā paṭhamena ṭhānena pāsaṃso."
320596,82,825,66,77,1,61,8,"‘ Saṃvibhajati puññāni karotī’ ti, iminā dutiyena ṭhānena pāsaṃso. "
320597,82,825,78,92,1,79,11,"Ayaṃ, gahapati, kāmabhogī iminā ekena ṭhānena gārayho, imehi dvīhi ṭhānehi pāsaṃso."
320598,82,826,2,43,1,272,34,"‘ ‘ Tatra, gahapati, yvāyaṃ kāmabhogī dhammādhammena bhoge pariyesati sāhasenapi asāhasenapi, dhammādhammena bhoge pariyesitvā sāhasenapi asāhasenapi na attānaṃ sukheti na pīṇeti na saṃvibhajati na puññāni karoti, ayaṃ, gahapati, kāmabhogī ekena ṭhānena pāsaṃso tīhi ṭhānehi gārayho."
320599,82,826,44,56,1,66,9,"‘ Dhammena bhoge pariyesati asāhasenā’ ti, iminā ekena ṭhānena pāsaṃso."
