320678,82,843,2,4,1,17,2,3 . Kiṃdiṭṭhikasuttaṃ 
320679,82,844,2,15,1,73,8,93. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
320680,82,844,16,26,1,86,10,Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati divā divassa sāvatthiyā nikkhami bhagavantaṃ dassanāya. 
320681,82,844,27,32,1,47,5,Atha kho anāthapiṇḍikassa gahapatissa etadahosi–
320682,82,844,33,40,1,36,5,‘‘ akālo kho tāva bhagavantaṃ dassanāya. 
320683,82,844,41,43,1,19,2,Paṭisallīno bhagavā. 
320684,82,844,44,48,1,45,4,Manobhāvanīyānampi bhikkhūnaṃ akālo dassanāya. 
320685,82,844,49,52,1,33,3,Paṭisallīnā manobhāvanīyā bhikkhū. 
320686,82,844,53,62,1,73,7,Yaṃnūnāhaṃ yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkameyyan’’ ti. 
320687,82,845,2,11,1,87,9,Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena aññatitthiyānaṃ paribbājakānaṃ ārāmo tenupasaṅkami. 
320688,82,845,12,27,1,147,15,Tena kho pana samayena aññatitthiyā paribbājakā saṅgamma samāgamma unnādino uccāsaddamahāsaddā anekavihitaṃ tiracchānakathaṃ kathentā nisinnā honti. 
320689,82,845,28,37,1,87,9,Addasaṃsu kho te aññatitthiyā paribbājakā anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ dūratova āgacchantaṃ. 
320690,82,845,38,41,1,30,3,Disvāna aññamaññaṃ saṇṭhāpesuṃ–
320691,82,845,42,51,1,46,6,"‘‘ appasaddā bhonto hontu, mā bhonto saddamakattha. "
320692,82,845,52,60,1,71,8,Ayaṃ anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati ārāmaṃ āgacchati samaṇassa gotamassa sāvako. 
320693,82,845,61,77,1,126,15,"Yāvatā kho pana samaṇassa gotamassa sāvakā gihī odātavasanā sāvatthiyaṃ paṭivasanti, ayaṃ tesaṃ aññataro anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati. "
320694,82,845,78,87,1,76,8,Appasaddakāmā kho pana te āyasmanto appasaddavinītā appasaddassa vaṇṇavādino. 
320695,82,845,88,98,1,67,8,Appeva nāma appasaddaṃ parisaṃ viditvā upasaṅkamitabbaṃ maññeyyā’’ ti. 
320696,82,846,2,10,1,49,7,Atha kho te aññatitthiyā paribbājakā tuṇhī ahesuṃ. 
320697,82,846,11,20,1,78,9,Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena te aññatitthiyā paribbājakā tenupasaṅkami; 
320698,82,846,21,27,1,63,6,upasaṅkamitvā tehi aññatitthiyehi paribbājakehi saddhiṃ sammodi. 
320699,82,846,28,35,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
320700,82,846,36,46,1,86,9,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ te aññatitthiyā paribbājakā etadavocuṃ–
320701,82,846,47,59,1,44,6,"‘‘ vadehi, gahapati, kiṃdiṭṭhiko samaṇo gotamo’’ ti?"
320702,82,846,60,75,1,53,9,"‘‘ Na kho ahaṃ, bhante, bhagavato sabbaṃ diṭṭhiṃ jānāmī’’ ti."
320703,82,847,2,16,1,67,11,"‘ ‘ Iti kira tvaṃ, gahapati, na samaṇassa gotamassa sabbaṃ diṭṭhiṃ jānāsi; "
320704,82,847,17,26,1,38,5,"vadehi, gahapati, kiṃdiṭṭhikā bhikkhū’’ ti?"
320705,82,847,27,42,1,56,9,"‘‘ Bhikkhūnampi kho ahaṃ, bhante, na sabbaṃ diṭṭhiṃ jānāmī’’ ti."
320706,82,848,2,21,1,105,16,"‘ ‘ Iti kira tvaṃ, gahapati, na samaṇassa gotamassa sabbaṃ diṭṭhiṃ jānāsi napi bhikkhūnaṃ sabbaṃ diṭṭhiṃ jānāsi; "
320707,82,848,22,31,1,38,5,"vadehi, gahapati, kiṃdiṭṭhikosi tuvan’’ ti?"
320708,82,848,32,45,1,61,9,"‘‘ Etaṃ kho, bhante, amhehi na dukkaraṃ byākātuṃ yaṃdiṭṭhikā mayaṃ. "
320709,82,848,46,64,1,128,15,"Iṅgha tāva āyasmanto yathāsakāni diṭṭhigatāni byākarontu, pacchāpetaṃ amhehi na dukkaraṃ bhavissati byākātuṃ yaṃdiṭṭhikā mayan’’ ti. "
320710,82,849,2,9,1,66,7,Evaṃ vutte aññataro paribbājako anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ etadavoca–
320711,82,849,10,26,1,71,9,"‘‘ sassato loko, idameva saccaṃ moghamaññanti– evaṃdiṭṭhiko ahaṃ, gahapatī’’ ti. "
320712,82,850,2,9,1,61,6,Aññataropi kho paribbājako anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ etadavoca–
320713,82,850,10,26,1,72,9,"‘‘ asassato loko, idameva saccaṃ moghamaññanti– evaṃdiṭṭhiko ahaṃ, gahapatī’’ ti. "
320714,82,851,2,8,1,61,6,Aññataropi kho paribbājako anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ etadavoca–
320715,82,851,9,69,1,280,45,"‘‘ antavā loko… pe… anantavā loko… taṃ jīvaṃ taṃ sarīraṃ… aññaṃ jīvaṃ aññaṃ sarīraṃ… hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā… na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā… hoti ca na ca hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā… neva hoti na na hoti tathāgato paraṃ maraṇā, idameva saccaṃ moghamaññanti– evaṃdiṭṭhiko ahaṃ, gahapatī’’ ti. "
320716,82,852,2,10,1,58,7,Evaṃ vutte anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati te paribbājake etadavoca–
320717,82,852,11,19,1,28,4,"‘‘ yvāyaṃ, bhante, āyasmā evamāha–"
320718,82,852,20,45,1,160,18,"‘ sassato loko, idameva saccaṃ moghamaññanti– evaṃdiṭṭhiko ahaṃ, gahapatī’ ti , imassa ayamāyasmato diṭṭhi attano vā ayonisomanasikārahetu uppannā paratoghosapaccayā vā. "
320719,82,852,46,54,1,62,8,Sā kho panesā diṭṭhi bhūtā saṅkhatā cetayitā paṭiccasamuppannā. 
