320740,82,855,51,73,1,82,14,"‘ Yaṃ dukkhaṃ taṃ netaṃ mama, nesohamasmi, na meso attā’ ti– evaṃdiṭṭhiko ahaṃ, bhante’’ ti."
320741,82,856,2,16,1,79,10,"‘ ‘ Yaṃ kho, gahapati, kiñci bhūtaṃ saṅkhataṃ cetayitaṃ paṭiccasamuppannaṃ tadaniccaṃ. "
