320825,82,876,2,4,1,12,2,5 . Uttiyasuttaṃ 
320826,82,877,2,14,1,54,7,95. Atha kho uttiyo paribbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
320827,82,877,15,19,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
320828,82,877,20,26,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
320829,82,877,27,34,1,62,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho uttiyo paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
