320831,82,877,55,64,1,30,5,"‘‘ Abyākataṃ kho etaṃ, uttiya, mayā–"
320832,82,877,65,76,1,42,6,"‘ sassato loko, idameva saccaṃ moghamaññan’’’ ti."
