320856,82,886,27,47,1,91,9,"Seyyathāpi, āvuso uttiya, rañño paccantimaṃ nagaraṃ daḷhuddhāpaṃ[ daḷhuddāpaṃ( sī. pī.)] daḷhapākāratoraṇaṃ ekadvāraṃ. "
