321343,82,1050,62,79,1,123,15,Ko nu kho imassa bhagavatā saṃkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajeyyā’’ ti? 
321344,82,1051,2,7,1,35,5,Atha kho tesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ etadahosi–
321345,82,1051,8,21,1,84,11,‘‘ ayaṃ kho āyasmā ānando satthu ceva saṃvaṇṇito sambhāvito ca viññūnaṃ sabrahmacārīnaṃ. 
321346,82,1051,22,36,1,132,14,Pahoti cāyasmā ānando imassa bhagavatā saṃkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajituṃ. 
321347,82,1051,37,42,1,49,5,Yaṃnūna mayaṃ yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkameyyāma; 
321348,82,1051,43,67,1,59,5,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyāma[ puccheyyāma( sī. syā. pī.) ma. ni.1.202 passitabbaṃ]. 
321349,82,1051,68,79,1,59,9,Yathā no āyasmā ānando byākarissati tathā naṃ dhāressāmā’’ ti. 
321350,82,1052,2,10,1,53,7,Atha kho te bhikkhū yenāyasmā ānando tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
321351,82,1052,11,16,1,50,5,upasaṅkamitvā āyasmatā ānandena saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu. 
321352,82,1052,17,23,1,61,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
321353,82,1052,24,33,1,62,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavocuṃ–
321354,82,1053,2,21,1,121,16,"‘ ‘ Idaṃ kho no, āvuso ānanda, bhagavā saṃkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho–"
321355,82,1053,22,32,1,38,6,‘ adhammo ca… pe… tathā paṭipajjitabban’ ti.
321356,82,1054,2,13,1,59,8,"‘ ‘ Tesaṃ no, āvuso, amhākaṃ acirapakkantassa bhagavato etadahosi–"
321357,82,1054,14,40,1,154,19,"‘ idaṃ kho no, āvuso, bhagavatā saṃkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho– adhammo ca… pe… tathā paṭipajjitabbanti. "
321358,82,1054,41,57,1,123,15,Ko nu kho imassa bhagavatā saṃkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa vitthārena atthaṃ vibhajeyyā’ ti?
321359,82,1055,2,11,1,32,6,"‘ ‘ Tesaṃ no, āvuso, amhākaṃ etadahosi–"
321360,82,1055,12,24,1,84,11,‘ ayaṃ kho āyasmā ānando satthu ceva saṃvaṇṇito sambhāvito ca viññūnaṃ sabrahmacārīnaṃ. 
