321365,82,1055,64,70,1,26,4,Vibhajatu āyasmā ānando’’ ti.
321366,82,1056,2,26,1,184,20,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi , āvuso, puriso sāratthiko sāragavesī sārapariyesanaṃ caramāno mahato rukkhassa tiṭṭhato sāravato atikkammeva mūlaṃ atikkamma khandhaṃ sākhāpalāse sāraṃ pariyesitabbaṃ maññeyya; "
321367,82,1056,27,38,1,119,11,evaṃsampadamidaṃ āyasmantānaṃ satthari sammukhībhūte taṃ bhagavantaṃ atisitvā amhe etamatthaṃ paṭipucchitabbaṃ maññatha. 
321368,82,1056,39,60,1,158,19,"So hāvuso, bhagavā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passati, cakkhubhūto ñāṇabhūto dhammabhūto brahmabhūto vattā pavattā atthassa ninnetā amatassa dātā dhammassāmī tathāgato. "
321369,82,1056,61,74,1,96,11,So ceva panetassa kālo ahosi yaṃ tumhe bhagavantaṃyeva upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyātha. 
321370,82,1056,75,85,1,52,8,Yathā vo bhagavā byākareyya tathā naṃ dhāreyyāthā’’ ti.
321371,82,1057,2,24,1,165,20,"‘ ‘ Addhāvuso ānanda, bhagavā jānaṃ jānāti passaṃ passati cakkhubhūto ñāṇabhūto dhammabhūto brahmabhūto vattā pavattā atthassa ninnetā amatassa dātā dhammassāmī tathāgato. "
321372,82,1057,25,44,1,144,18,"So ceva panetassa kālo ahosi yaṃ mayaṃ bhagavantaṃyeva upasaṅkamitvā etamatthaṃ paṭipuccheyyāma, yathā no bhagavā byākareyya tathā naṃ dhāreyyāma. "
