321402,82,1064,2,21,1,114,15,"‘ ‘ Ayaṃ kho no, āvuso, bhagavā saṃkhittena uddesaṃ uddisitvā vitthārena atthaṃ avibhajitvā uṭṭhāyāsanā vihāraṃ paviṭṭho–"
321403,82,1064,22,56,1,196,25,"‘ adhammo ca, bhikkhave, veditabbo dhammo ca… pe… tathā paṭipajjitabban’ ti, imassa kho ahaṃ, āvuso, bhagavatā saṃkhittena uddesassa uddiṭṭhassa vitthārena atthaṃ avibhattassa evaṃ vitthārena atthaṃ ājānāmi. "
