321841,82,1219,1,7,1,14,1,(17)2. Jāṇussoṇivaggo
321842,82,1220,2,4,1,25,2,1 . Brāhmaṇapaccorohaṇīsuttaṃ 
321843,82,1221,2,25,1,153,18,167. Tena kho pana samayena jāṇussoṇi brāhmaṇo tadahuposathe sīsaṃnhāto navaṃ khomayugaṃ nivattho allakusamuṭṭhiṃ ādāya bhagavato avidūre ekamantaṃ ṭhito hoti. 
321844,82,1222,2,16,1,131,14,Addasā kho bhagavā jāṇussoṇiṃ brāhmaṇaṃ tadahuposathe sīsaṃnhātaṃ navaṃ khomayugaṃ nivatthaṃ allakusamuṭṭhiṃ ādāya ekamantaṃ ṭhitaṃ. 
321845,82,1222,17,21,1,38,4,Disvāna jāṇussoṇiṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavoca–
321846,82,1222,22,39,1,109,13,"‘‘ kiṃ nu tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, tadahuposathe sīsaṃnhāto navaṃ khomayugaṃ nivattho allakusamuṭṭhiṃ ādāya ekamantaṃ ṭhito? "
321847,82,1222,40,46,1,29,4,Kiṃ nvajja brāhmaṇakulassā’’ ti?
321848,82,1222,47,60,1,46,6,"‘‘ Paccorohaṇī, bho gotama, ajja brāhmaṇakulassā’’ ti ."
321849,82,1223,2,16,1,58,9,"‘ ‘ Yathā kathaṃ pana, brāhmaṇa, brāhmaṇānaṃ paccorohaṇī hotī’’ ti?"
321850,82,1223,17,45,1,190,24,"‘‘ Idha, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā tadahuposathe sīsaṃnhātā navaṃ khomayugaṃ nivatthā allena gomayena pathaviṃ opuñjitvā haritehi kusehi pattharitvā antarā ca velaṃ antarā ca agyāgāraṃ seyyaṃ kappenti. "
321851,82,1223,46,55,1,63,8,Te taṃ rattiṃ tikkhattuṃ paccuṭṭhāya pañjalikā aggiṃ namassanti–
321852,82,1223,56,64,1,46,5,"‘ paccorohāma bhavantaṃ, paccorohāma bhavantan’ ti. "
321853,82,1223,65,70,1,49,5,Bahukena ca sappitelanavanītena aggiṃ santappenti. 
321854,82,1223,71,80,1,79,9,Tassā ca rattiyā accayena paṇītena khādanīyena bhojanīyena brāhmaṇe santappenti. 
