322176,82,1330,2,36,1,85,11,176. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā pāvāyaṃ[ campāyaṃ( ka. sī.) dī. ni.2.189 passitabbaṃ] viharati cundassa kammāraputtassa ambavane. 
322177,82,1330,37,44,1,54,7,Atha kho cundo kammāraputto yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
322178,82,1330,45,50,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
322179,82,1330,51,59,1,61,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho cundaṃ kammāraputtaṃ bhagavā etadavoca–
322180,82,1330,60,73,1,39,7,"‘‘ kassa no tvaṃ, cunda, soceyyāni rocesī’’ ti?"
322181,82,1330,74,98,1,102,9,"‘‘ Brāhmaṇā, bhante, pacchābhūmakā kamaṇḍalukā sevālamālikā[ sevālamālakā( sī. syā. pī.)] aggiparicārikā udakorohakā soceyyāni paññapenti; "
322182,82,1330,99,105,1,27,4,tesāhaṃ soceyyāni rocemī’’ ti.
322183,82,1331,2,21,1,122,14,"‘ ‘ Yathā kathaṃ pana, cunda, brāhmaṇā pacchābhūmakā kamaṇḍalukā sevālamālikā aggiparicārikā udakorohakā soceyyāni paññapentī’’ ti?"
322184,82,1331,22,34,1,86,8,"‘‘ Idha, bhante, brāhmaṇā pacchābhūmakā kamaṇḍalukā sevālamālikā aggiparicārikā udakorohakā. "
322185,82,1331,35,48,1,27,4,Te sāvakaṃ[ sāvake( syā. ka.)] evaṃ samādapenti–
322186,82,1331,49,83,1,74,9,"‘ ehi tvaṃ, ambho purisa, kālasseva[ sakālasseva( syā.)] uṭṭhahantova[ uṭṭhahanto( syā.), vuṭṭhahantova( pī. ka.)] sayanamhā pathaviṃ āmaseyyāsi; "
322187,82,1331,84,92,1,52,7,"no ce pathaviṃ āmaseyyāsi, allāni gomayāni āmaseyyāsi; "
322188,82,1331,93,103,1,59,8,"no ce allāni gomayāni āmaseyyāsi, haritāni tiṇāni āmaseyyāsi; "
322189,82,1331,104,112,1,52,7,"no ce haritāni tiṇāni āmaseyyāsi, aggiṃ paricareyyāsi; "
322190,82,1331,113,121,1,56,7,"no ce aggiṃ paricareyyāsi, pañjaliko ādiccaṃ namasseyyāsi; "
322191,82,1331,122,133,1,71,9,"no ce pañjaliko ādiccaṃ namasseyyāsi, sāyatatiyakaṃ udakaṃ oroheyyāsī’ ti. "
322192,82,1331,134,148,1,111,11,"Evaṃ kho, bhante, brāhmaṇā pacchābhūmakā kamaṇḍalukā sevālamālikā aggiparicārikā udakorohakā soceyyāni paññapenti; "
322193,82,1331,149,155,1,27,4,tesāhaṃ soceyyāni rocemī’’ ti.
322194,82,1332,2,29,1,162,20,"‘ ‘ Aññathā kho, cunda, brāhmaṇā pacchābhūmakā kamaṇḍalukā sevālamālikā aggiparicārikā udakorohakā soceyyāni paññapenti, aññathā ca pana ariyassa vinaye soceyyaṃ hotī’’ ti."
