322263,82,1357,2,29,1,144,23,"‘ ‘ Pisuṇaṃ vācaṃ pahāya, pisuṇāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti– na ito sutvā amutra akkhātā imesaṃ bhedāya, na amutra vā sutvā imesaṃ akkhātā amūsaṃ bhedāya. "
322264,82,1357,30,44,1,120,14,Iti bhinnānaṃ vā sandhātā sahitānaṃ vā anuppadātā samaggārāmo samaggarato samagganandī samaggakaraṇiṃ vācaṃ bhāsitā hoti.
322265,82,1358,2,12,1,54,8,"‘ ‘ Pharusaṃ vācaṃ pahāya, pharusāya vācāya paṭivirato hoti. "
322266,82,1358,13,28,1,111,14,"Yā sā vācā nelā kaṇṇasukhā pemanīyā hadayaṅgamā porī bahujanakantā bahujanamanāpā, tathārūpiṃ vācaṃ bhāsitā hoti."
322267,82,1359,2,16,1,102,11,"‘ ‘ Samphappalāpaṃ pahāya, samphappalāpā paṭivirato hoti kālavādī bhūtavādī atthavādī dhammavādī vinayavādī; "
322268,82,1359,17,25,1,77,8,nidhānavatiṃ vācaṃ bhāsitā hoti kālena sāpadesaṃ pariyantavatiṃ atthasaṃhitaṃ. 
322269,82,1359,26,36,1,47,7,"Evaṃ kho, cunda , catubbidhaṃ vācāya soceyyaṃ hoti."
322270,82,1360,2,13,1,44,7,"‘ ‘ Kathañca , cunda, tividhaṃ manasā soceyyaṃ hoti? "
322271,82,1360,14,21,1,35,5,"Idha, cunda, ekacco anabhijjhālu hoti. "
322272,82,1360,22,29,1,56,7,Yaṃ taṃ parassa paravittūpakaraṇaṃ taṃ anabhijjhitā hoti–
322273,82,1360,30,39,1,35,7,‘ aho vata yaṃ parassa taṃ mamassā’ ti.
322274,82,1361,2,7,1,42,4,‘ ‘ Abyāpannacitto hoti appaduṭṭhamanasaṅkappo–
322275,82,1361,8,42,1,67,10,"‘ ime sattā averā hontu[ idaṃ padaṃ sī. syā. pī. potthakesu natthi, tathā ma. ni.1.441] abyāpajjā, anīghā sukhī attānaṃ pariharantū’ ti."
322276,82,1362,2,8,1,35,4,‘ ‘ Sammādiṭṭhiko hoti aviparītadassano–
322277,82,1362,9,59,1,281,39,"‘ atthi dinnaṃ, atthi yiṭṭhaṃ, atthi hutaṃ, atthi sukaṭadukkaṭānaṃ kammānaṃ phalaṃ vipāko, atthi ayaṃ loko, atthi paro loko, atthi mātā, atthi pitā, atthi sattā opapātikā, atthi loke samaṇabrāhmaṇā sammaggatā sammāpaṭipannā ye imañca lokaṃ parañca lokaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedentī’ ti. "
322278,82,1362,60,69,1,44,7,"Evaṃ kho, cunda, tividhaṃ manasā soceyyaṃ hoti."
