322682,82,1517,2,31,1,95,9,"217.‘‘ Nāhaṃ , bhikkhave, sañcetanikānaṃ kammānaṃ katānaṃ upacitānaṃ appaṭisaṃveditvā[ appaṭisaṃviditvā( sī. syā. pī.)] byantībhāvaṃ vadāmi. "
322683,82,1517,32,69,1,55,9,"Tañca kho diṭṭheva dhamme upapajje vā[ upapajjaṃ vā( ka.) a. ni.6.63 passitabbaṃ, upapajja vā( ma. ni.3.303)] apare vā pariyāye. "
