322961,83,5,2,4,1,16,2,1 . Kimatthiyasuttaṃ 
322962,83,6,2,30,1,87,11,1.[ a. ni.10.1] Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme. 
322963,83,6,31,39,1,49,7,Atha kho āyasmā ānando yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
322964,83,6,40,45,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
322965,83,6,46,53,1,57,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā ānando bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
322966,83,6,54,66,1,52,6,"‘‘ kimatthiyāni, bhante, kusalāni sīlāni kimānisaṃsānī’’ ti?"
322967,83,6,67,80,1,70,7,"‘‘ Avippaṭisāratthāni kho, ānanda, kusalāni sīlāni avippaṭisārānisaṃsānī’’ ti."
322968,83,7,2,14,1,47,6,"‘ ‘ Avippaṭisāro pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimānisaṃso’’?"
322969,83,7,15,26,1,50,5,"‘‘ Avippaṭisāro kho, ānanda, pāmojjattho pāmojjānisaṃso’’."
322970,83,8,2,13,1,45,6,"‘ ‘ Pāmojjaṃ pana, bhante, kimatthiyaṃ kimānisaṃsaṃ’’?"
322971,83,8,14,25,1,42,5,"‘‘ Pāmojjaṃ kho, ānanda, pītatthaṃ pītānisaṃsaṃ’’."
322972,83,9,2,13,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Pīti pana, bhante, kimatthiyā kimānisaṃsā’’?"
322973,83,9,14,25,1,46,5,"‘‘ Pīti kho, ānanda, passaddhatthā passaddhānisaṃsā’’."
322974,83,10,2,13,1,44,6,"‘ ‘ Passaddhi pana, bhante, kimatthiyā kimānisaṃsā’’?"
322975,83,10,14,25,1,43,5,"‘‘ Passaddhi kho, ānanda, sukhatthā sukhānisaṃsā’’."
322976,83,11,2,13,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Sukhaṃ pana, bhante, kimatthiyaṃ kimānisaṃsaṃ’’?"
322977,83,11,14,25,1,46,5,"‘‘ Sukhaṃ kho, ānanda, samādhatthaṃ samādhānisaṃsaṃ’’."
322978,83,12,2,14,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Samādhi pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimānisaṃso’’?"
322979,83,12,15,27,1,73,5,"‘‘ Samādhi kho, ānanda, yathābhūtañāṇadassanattho yathābhūtañāṇadassanānisaṃso’’ ."
322980,83,13,2,13,1,59,6,"‘ ‘ Yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ pana, bhante, kimatthiyaṃ kimānisaṃsaṃ’’?"
322981,83,13,14,25,1,62,5,"‘‘ Yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ kho, ānanda, nibbidatthaṃ nibbidānisaṃsaṃ’’."
322982,83,14,2,14,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Nibbidā, pana, bhante, kimatthiyā kimānisaṃsā’’?"
322983,83,14,15,27,1,43,5,"‘‘ Nibbidā kho, ānanda, virāgatthā virāgānisaṃsā ’’."
322984,83,15,2,13,1,41,6,"‘ ‘ Virāgo pana, bhante, kimatthiyo kimānisaṃso’’?"
322985,83,15,14,23,1,66,5,"‘‘ Virāgo kho, ānanda, vimuttiñāṇadassanattho vimuttiñāṇadassanānisaṃso."
322986,83,16,2,50,1,452,35,"‘ ‘ Iti kho, ānanda, kusalāni sīlāni avippaṭisāratthāni avippaṭisārānisaṃsāni, avippaṭisāro pāmojjattho pāmojjānisaṃso, pāmojjaṃ pītatthaṃ pītānisaṃsaṃ, pīti passaddhatthā passaddhānisaṃsā, passaddhi sukhatthā sukhānisaṃsā, sukhaṃ samādhatthaṃ samādhānisaṃsaṃ, samādhi yathābhūtañāṇadassanattho yathābhūtañāṇadassanānisaṃso, yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ nibbidatthaṃ nibbidānisaṃsaṃ, nibbidā virāgatthā virāgānisaṃsā, virāgo vimuttiñāṇadassanattho vimuttiñāṇadassanānisaṃso. "
322987,83,16,51,64,1,59,9,"Iti kho, ānanda, kusalāni sīlāni anupubbena aggāya parentī’’ ti. "
322988,83,16,65,66,1,8,1,Paṭhamaṃ.
322989,83,17,2,4,1,20,2,2 . Cetanākaraṇīyasuttaṃ 
322990,83,18,2,25,1,56,6,"2.[ a. ni.10.2]‘‘ Sīlavato, bhikkhave, sīlasampannassa na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
322991,83,18,26,32,1,28,4,‘ avippaṭisāro me uppajjatū’ ti. 
322992,83,18,33,43,1,74,8,"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ sīlavato sīlasampannassa avippaṭisāro uppajjati."
322993,83,19,2,11,1,47,6,"‘ ‘ Avippaṭisārissa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
322994,83,19,12,18,1,24,4,‘ pāmojjaṃ me uppajjatū’ ti. 
322995,83,19,19,28,1,61,7,"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ avippaṭisārissa pāmojjaṃ uppajjati."
322996,83,20,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Pamuditassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
322997,83,20,12,18,1,20,4,‘ pīti me uppajjatū’ ti. 
322998,83,20,19,28,1,53,7,"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ pamuditassa pīti uppajjati."
322999,83,21,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Pītimanassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
323000,83,21,12,19,1,22,4,‘ kāyo me passambhatū’ ti. 
323001,83,21,20,29,1,55,7,"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ pītimanassa kāyo passambhati."
323002,83,22,2,12,1,48,6,"‘ ‘ Passaddhakāyassa , bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
323003,83,22,13,18,1,18,3,‘ sukhaṃ vediyāmī’ ti. 
323004,83,22,19,28,1,56,7,"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ vediyati."
323005,83,23,2,11,1,39,6,"‘ ‘ Sukhino, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
323006,83,23,12,18,1,24,4,‘ cittaṃ me samādhiyatū’ ti. 
323007,83,23,19,28,1,53,7,"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
323008,83,24,2,12,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Samāhitassa , bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
323009,83,24,13,19,1,29,4,‘ yathābhūtaṃ jānāmi passāmī’ ti. 
323010,83,24,20,31,1,62,8,"Dhammatā esā , bhikkhave, yaṃ samāhito yathābhūtaṃ jānāti passati."
323011,83,25,2,13,1,58,8,"‘ ‘ Yathābhūtaṃ, bhikkhave, jānato passato na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
323012,83,25,14,18,1,13,2,‘ nibbindāmī’ ti. 
323013,83,25,19,29,1,62,8,"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ yathābhūtaṃ jānaṃ passaṃ nibbindati."
323014,83,26,2,11,1,43,6,"‘ ‘ Nibbinnassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
323015,83,26,12,16,1,12,2,‘ virajjāmī’ ti. 
323016,83,26,17,25,1,45,6,"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ nibbinno virajjati."
323017,83,27,2,11,1,42,6,"‘ ‘ Virattassa, bhikkhave, na cetanāya karaṇīyaṃ–"
323018,83,27,12,17,1,35,3,‘ vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ sacchikaromī’ ti. 
323019,83,27,18,27,1,67,7,"Dhammatā esā, bhikkhave, yaṃ viratto vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ sacchikaroti."
323020,83,28,2,49,1,455,35,"‘ ‘ Iti kho, bhikkhave, virāgo vimuttiñāṇadassanattho vimuttiñāṇadassanānisaṃso, nibbidā virāgatthā virāgānisaṃsā, yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ nibbidatthaṃ nibbidānisaṃsaṃ, samādhi yathābhūtañāṇadassanattho yathābhūtañāṇadassanānisaṃso, sukhaṃ samādhatthaṃ samādhānisaṃsaṃ, passaddhi sukhatthā sukhānisaṃsā, pīti passaddhatthā passaddhānisaṃsā, pāmojjaṃ pītatthaṃ pītānisaṃsaṃ, avippaṭisāro pāmojjattho pāmojjānisaṃso, kusalāni sīlāni avippaṭisāratthāni avippaṭisārānisaṃsāni. "
323021,83,28,50,69,1,94,13,"Iti kho, bhikkhave, dhammā dhamme abhisandenti, dhammā dhamme paripūrenti apārā pāraṃ gamanāyā’’ ti. "
323022,83,28,70,71,1,7,1,Dutiyaṃ.
323023,83,29,2,4,1,20,2,3 . Paṭhamaupanisāsuttaṃ 
323024,83,30,2,29,1,64,6,"3.[ a. ni.5.24;10.3]‘‘ Dussīlassa, bhikkhave, sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti avippaṭisāro. "
323025,83,30,30,36,1,67,6,Avippaṭisāre asati avippaṭisāravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti pāmojjaṃ. 
323026,83,30,37,43,1,52,6,Pāmojje asati pāmojjavipannassa hatūpanisā hoti pīti. 
323027,83,30,44,50,1,53,6,Pītiyā asati pītivipannassa hatūpanisā hoti passaddhi. 
323028,83,30,51,59,1,61,6,Passaddhiyā asati passaddhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti sukhaṃ. 
323029,83,30,60,66,1,56,6,Sukhe asati sukhavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti sammāsamādhi. 
323030,83,30,67,73,1,84,6,Sammāsamādhimhi asati sammāsamādhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ. 
323031,83,30,74,81,1,83,6,Yathābhūtañāṇadassane asati yathābhūtañāṇadassanavipannassa hatūpanisā hoti nibbidā. 
323032,83,30,82,88,1,56,6,Nibbidāya asati nibbidāvipannassa hatūpaniso hoti virāgo. 
323033,83,30,89,95,1,66,6,Virāge asati virāgavipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ.
323034,83,31,2,10,1,46,5,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, rukkho sākhāpalāsavipanno. "
323035,83,31,11,25,1,83,11,"Tassa papaṭikāpi na pāripūriṃ gacchati, tacopi… pheggupi… sāropi na pāripūriṃ gacchati. "
323036,83,31,26,47,1,168,16,"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, dussīlassa sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti avippaṭisāro, avippaṭisāre asati avippaṭisāravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti pāmojjaṃ… pe… vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
323037,83,32,2,76,1,700,61,"‘ ‘ Sīlavato, bhikkhave, sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti avippaṭisāro, avippaṭisāre sati avippaṭisārasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti pāmojjaṃ, pāmojje sati pāmojjasampannassa upanisasampannā hoti pīti, pītiyā sati pītisampannassa upanisasampannā hoti passaddhi, passaddhiyā sati passaddhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti sukhaṃ, sukhe sati sukhasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti sammāsamādhi, sammāsamādhimhi sati sammāsamādhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ, yathābhūtañāṇadassane sati yathābhūtañāṇadassanasampannassa upanisasampannā hoti nibbidā, nibbidāya sati nibbidāsampannassa upanisasampanno hoti virāgo, virāge sati virāgasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ."
323038,83,33,2,10,1,47,5,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, rukkho sākhāpalāsasampanno. "
323039,83,33,11,23,1,77,9,"Tassa papaṭikāpi pāripūriṃ gacchati, tacopi… pheggupi… sāropi pāripūriṃ gacchati. "
323040,83,33,24,47,1,171,16,"Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sīlavato sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti avippaṭisāro, avippaṭisāre sati avippaṭisārasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti… pe… vimuttiñāṇadassanan’’ ti. "
