323043,83,35,2,14,1,43,6,4. Tatra kho āyasmā sāriputto bhikkhū āmantesi–
323044,83,35,15,42,1,18,3,‘‘ āvuso bhikkhave’’ ti[ bhikkhavoti( sī. syā. pī.) evaṃ sabbattha a. ni.10.4].
323045,83,35,43,55,1,57,8,‘‘ Āvuso’’ ti kho te bhikkhū āyasmato sāriputtassa paccassosuṃ. 
