323117,83,67,2,4,1,12,2,9 . Saddhasuttaṃ 
323118,83,68,2,13,1,51,6,9. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā nātike viharati giñjakāvasathe . 
323119,83,68,14,22,1,49,7,Atha kho āyasmā saddho yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
