323285,83,108,2,20,1,43,6,"[ a. ni.6.9]‘‘ Idha tvaṃ, mahānāma, tathāgataṃ anussareyyāsi–"
323286,83,108,21,34,1,59,9,‘ itipi so bhagavā… pe… satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti. 
323287,83,108,35,60,1,174,20,"Yasmiṃ, mahānāma, samaye ariyasāvako tathāgataṃ anussarati, nevassa tasmiṃ samaye rāgapariyuṭṭhitaṃ cittaṃ hoti, na dosapariyuṭṭhitaṃ cittaṃ hoti, na mohapariyuṭṭhitaṃ cittaṃ hoti; "
323288,83,108,61,69,1,59,7,ujugatamevassa tasmiṃ samaye cittaṃ hoti tathāgataṃ ārabbha. 
323289,83,108,70,86,1,115,12,"Ujugatacitto kho pana, mahānāma, ariyasāvako labhati atthavedaṃ, labhati dhammavedaṃ, labhati dhammūpasaṃhitaṃ pāmojjaṃ. "
323290,83,108,87,102,1,109,12,"Pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ vediyati, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati. "
323291,83,108,103,129,1,204,19,"Imaṃ kho tvaṃ, mahānāma, buddhānussatiṃ gacchantopi bhāveyyāsi, ṭhitopi bhāveyyāsi, nisinnopi bhāveyyāsi, sayānopi bhāveyyāsi, kammantaṃ adhiṭṭhahantopi bhāveyyāsi, puttasambādhasayanaṃ ajjhāvasantopi bhāveyyāsi."
