323361,83,123,64,97,1,97,12,"‘‘ Saddho nāmāyaṃ, bhante, bhikkhu, sudattassa[ saddhassa( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] upāsakassa putto, saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito’’ ti."
323362,83,124,2,23,1,130,16,"‘ ‘ Kacci panāyaṃ, subhūti, saddho bhikkhu sudattassa upāsakassa putto saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito sandissati saddhāpadānesū’’ ti?"
