323364,83,124,32,43,1,64,8,"etassa, sugata, kālo, yaṃ bhagavā saddhassa saddhāpadānāni bhāseyya. "
323365,83,124,44,58,1,79,12,Idānāhaṃ jānissāmi yadi vā ayaṃ bhikkhu sandissati saddhāpadānesu yadi vā no’’ ti.
