323446,83,158,2,35,1,212,25,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, gahapati, bhikkhu vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ… pe… tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ… pe… catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
323447,83,158,36,39,1,22,3,So iti paṭisañcikkhati–
