323480,83,162,48,60,1,87,10,‘ Yaṃ kho pana kiñci abhisaṅkhataṃ abhisañcetayitaṃ tadaniccaṃ nirodhadhamman’ ti pajānāti. 
323481,83,162,61,67,1,40,6,So tattha ṭhito āsavānaṃ khayaṃ pāpuṇāti; 
323482,83,162,68,89,1,178,20,"no ce āsavānaṃ khayaṃ pāpuṇāti, teneva dhammarāgena tāya dhammanandiyā pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā opapātiko hoti tattha parinibbāyī anāvattidhammo tasmā lokā. "
323483,83,162,90,110,1,97,13,"Ayampi kho, gahapati, tena bhagavatā jānatā… pe… ananuppattaṃ vā anuttaraṃ yogakkhemaṃ anupāpuṇātī’’ ti. "
323484,83,163,2,10,1,69,8,Evaṃ vutte dasamo gahapati aṭṭhakanāgaro āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca–
323485,83,163,11,31,1,102,11,"‘‘ seyyathāpi, bhante ānanda, puriso ekaṃ nidhimukhaṃ gavesanto sakideva[ sabbatthapi evameva dissati] ekādasa nidhimukhāni adhigaccheyya; "
323486,83,163,32,84,1,99,12,"evamevaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, ekaṃ amatadvāraṃ gavesanto sakideva ekādasa amatadvārāni[ ekādasannaṃ amatadvārānaṃ( sabbattha) ma. ni.2.21 passitabbaṃ] alatthaṃ sevanāya[ savanāya( syā.) sī. pī. majjhimapaṇṇāsakadutiyasuttepi, bhāvanāya( ma. ni.2.21)]. "
323487,83,163,85,93,1,49,6,"Seyyathāpi, bhante, purisassa agāraṃ ekādasa dvāraṃ. "
323488,83,163,94,107,1,75,10,So tasmiṃ agāre āditte ekamekenapi dvārena sakkuṇeyya attānaṃ sotthiṃ kātuṃ; 
323489,83,163,108,123,1,117,13,"evamevaṃ kho ahaṃ, bhante, imesaṃ ekādasannaṃ amatadvārānaṃ ekamekenapi amatadvārena sakkuṇissāmi attānaṃ sotthiṃ kātuṃ. "
323490,83,163,124,134,1,71,8,"Ime hi nāma, bhante, aññatitthiyā ācariyassa ācariyadhanaṃ pariyesissanti. "
323491,83,163,135,157,1,52,8,Kiṃ[ kimaṅgaṃ( ma. ni.2.21)] panāhaṃ āyasmato ānandassa pūjaṃ na karissāmī’’ ti! 
323492,83,164,2,17,1,162,15,Atha kho dasamo gahapati aṭṭhakanāgaro vesālikañca pāṭaliputtakañca bhikkhusaṅghaṃ sannipātāpetvā paṇītena khādanīyena bhojanīyena sahatthā santappesi sampavāresi. 
323493,83,164,18,27,1,82,8,"Ekamekañca bhikkhuṃ paccekaṃ dussayugena acchādesi, āyasmantañca ānandaṃ ticīvarena. "
