323505,83,168,13,52,1,122,14,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu yaṃ kiñci rūpaṃ ()[( sabbaṃ rūpaṃ) ma. ni.1.347() katthaci dissati]‘ cattāri mahābhūtāni, catunnañca mahābhūtānaṃ upādāyarūpan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ nappajānāti. "
