323514,83,171,14,25,1,78,9,"Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu cakkhunā rūpaṃ disvā nimittaggāhī hoti anubyañjanaggāhī; "
323515,83,171,26,41,1,139,13,"yatvādhikaraṇamenaṃ cakkhundriyaṃ asaṃvutaṃ viharantaṃ abhijjhādomanassā pāpakā akusalā dhammā anvāssaveyyuṃ, tassa saṃvarāya na paṭipajjati; "
323516,83,171,42,49,1,57,6,"na rakkhati cakkhundriyaṃ, cakkhundriye saṃvaraṃ nāpajjati. "
