324853,85,43,2,72,1,230,27,"15.‘‘ Yasmiṃ , bhikkhave, adhikaraṇe āpanno[ āpattāpanno( ka.)] ca bhikkhu codako ca bhikkhu na sādhukaṃ attanāva attānaṃ paccavekkhati tasmetaṃ, bhikkhave, adhikaraṇe pāṭikaṅkhaṃ dīghattāya kharattāya vāḷattāya saṃvattissati, bhikkhū ca na phāsuṃ[ na phāsu( ka.)] viharissantīti[ viharissanti( sī. syā. kaṃ. ka.)]. "
324854,85,43,73,105,1,233,27,"Yasmiñca kho, bhikkhave, adhikaraṇe āpanno ca bhikkhu codako ca bhikkhu sādhukaṃ attanāva attānaṃ paccavekkhati tasmetaṃ, bhikkhave, adhikaraṇe pāṭikaṅkhaṃ na dīghattāya kharattāya vāḷattāya saṃvattissati, bhikkhū ca phāsuṃ viharissantīti."
324855,85,44,2,14,1,73,9,"‘ ‘ Kathañca, bhikkhave, āpanno bhikkhu sādhukaṃ attanāva attānaṃ paccavekkhati? "
324856,85,44,15,23,1,49,6,"Idha, bhikkhave, āpanno bhikkhu iti paṭisañcikkhati–"
324857,85,44,24,39,1,47,7,‘ ahaṃ kho akusalaṃ āpanno kañcideva[ kiñcideva( ka.)] desaṃ kāyena. 
324858,85,44,40,60,1,65,9,Maṃ so[ tasmā maṃ so( sī. syā.)] bhikkhu addasa akusalaṃ āpajjamānaṃ kiñcideva desaṃ kāyena. 
324859,85,44,61,80,1,124,18,"No ce ahaṃ akusalaṃ āpajjeyyaṃ kiñcideva desaṃ kāyena, na maṃ so bhikkhu passeyya akusalaṃ āpajjamānaṃ kiñcideva desaṃ kāyena. "
324860,85,44,81,102,1,128,19,"Yasmā ca kho, ahaṃ akusalaṃ āpanno kiñcideva desaṃ kāyena, tasmā maṃ so bhikkhu addasa akusalaṃ āpajjamānaṃ kiñcideva desaṃ kāyena. "
