326229,86,56,21,23,1,9,2,So suṇāti–
326230,86,56,24,33,1,66,7,‘ itthannāmo kira khattiyo khattiyehi khattiyābhisekena abhisitto’ ti. 
326231,86,56,34,38,1,18,4,Tassa na evaṃ hoti–
326232,86,56,39,48,1,64,7,‘ kudāssu nāma mampi khattiyā khattiyābhisekena abhisiñcissantī’ ti! 
326233,86,56,49,52,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
326234,86,56,53,76,1,68,8,"Yā hissa, bhikkhave, pubbe anabhisittassa abhisekāsā sā[ sāssa( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] paṭippassaddhā. "
