326472,86,110,79,84,1,57,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. 
326473,86,110,85,106,1,153,19,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā sāriputto yāvatako ahosi āyasmatā ca samiddhena āyasmatā ca mahākoṭṭhikena saddhiṃ kathāsallāpo taṃ sabbaṃ bhagavato ārocesi.
326474,86,111,2,13,1,47,7,"‘ ‘ Na khvettha, sāriputta, sukaraṃ ekaṃsena byākātuṃ–"
326475,86,111,14,25,1,64,9,‘ ayaṃ imesaṃ tiṇṇaṃ puggalānaṃ abhikkantataro ca paṇītataro cā’ ti. 
326476,86,111,26,80,1,207,26,"Ṭhānañhetaṃ, sāriputta, vijjati yvāyaṃ puggalo saddhāvimutto svāssa[ svāyaṃ( syā. kaṃ. pī.), soyaṃ( ka.)] arahattāya paṭipanno, yvāyaṃ puggalo kāyasakkhī svāssa sakadāgāmī vā anāgāmī vā, yo cāyaṃ puggalo diṭṭhippatto sopassa[ soyaṃ( ka.)] sakadāgāmī vā anāgāmī vā."
