326540,86,134,62,112,1,93,11,"Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, duṭṭhāruko[ duṭṭhārukā( sī.)] kaṭṭhena vā kaṭhalāya[ kathalāya( syā. kaṃ. ka.), kaṭhalena-kathalena( aṭṭhakathā)] vā ghaṭṭito[ ghaṭṭitā( sī.)] bhiyyosomattāya āsavaṃ deti[ assavanoti( sī.)]; "
