327018,86,310,55,83,1,53,7,"Na kho panassāhaṃ, bhikkhave, akāsikaṃ candanaṃ dhāremi[ kāsikaṃ candanaṃ dhāremi( syā. kaṃ. ka.), akāsikaṃ dhāremi(?)]. "
