327064,86,328,82,89,1,70,7,Appeva nāma imassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa antakiriyā paññāyethāti. 
327065,86,328,90,139,1,140,20,"Ahañceva kho pana yādisake [ yādisake vā( sī. pī. ka.)] kāme ohāya agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito tādisake vā[ ca( ka.)] kāme pariyeseyyaṃ tato vā[ ca( ka.)] pāpiṭṭhatare, na metaṃ patirūpan’ ti. "
327066,86,328,140,143,1,22,3,So iti paṭisañcikkhati–
327067,86,328,144,166,1,128,17,"‘ āraddhaṃ kho pana me vīriyaṃ bhavissati asallīnaṃ, upaṭṭhitā sati asammuṭṭhā, passaddho kāyo asāraddho, samāhitaṃ cittaṃ ekaggan’ ti. "
327068,86,328,167,186,1,129,15,"So attānaṃyeva adhipatiṃ karitvā akusalaṃ pajahati, kusalaṃ bhāveti, sāvajjaṃ pajahati, anavajjaṃ bhāveti, suddhaṃ attānaṃ pariharati. "
327069,86,328,187,193,1,38,4,"Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, attādhipateyyaṃ."
