327075,86,329,61,70,1,71,8,Appeva nāma imassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa antakiriyā paññāyethā’ ti. 
327076,86,329,71,95,1,160,19,"Ahañceva kho pana evaṃ pabbajito samāno kāmavitakkaṃ vā vitakkeyyaṃ, byāpādavitakkaṃ vā vitakkeyyaṃ, vihiṃsāvitakkaṃ vā vitakkeyyaṃ, mahā kho panāyaṃ lokasannivāso. "
327077,86,329,96,105,1,96,9,Mahantasmiṃ kho pana lokasannivāse santi samaṇabrāhmaṇā iddhimanto dibbacakkhukā paracittaviduno. 
327078,86,329,106,124,1,67,9,"Te dūratopi passanti, āsannāpi na dissanti, cetasāpi cittaṃ pajānanti[ jānanti( ka.)]. "
327079,86,329,125,129,1,22,4,Tepi maṃ evaṃ jāneyyuṃ–
327080,86,329,130,150,1,120,15,"‘ passatha, bho, imaṃ kulaputtaṃ saddhā agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajito samāno vokiṇṇo viharati pāpakehi akusalehi dhammehī’ ti. "
327081,86,329,151,157,1,65,6,Devatāpi kho santi iddhimantiniyo dibbacakkhukā paracittaviduniyo. 
327082,86,329,158,169,1,65,9,"Tā dūratopi passanti, āsannāpi na dissanti, cetasāpi cittaṃ jānanti. "
