327352,86,443,24,38,1,100,10,"‘‘ sutaṃ metaṃ, bho gotama, pubbakānaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ vuddhānaṃ mahallakānaṃ ācariyapācariyānaṃ bhāsamānānaṃ–"
327353,86,443,39,67,1,97,12,"‘ pubbe sudaṃ[ pubbassudaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] ayaṃ loko avīci maññe phuṭo ahosi manussehi, kukkuṭasaṃpātikā gāmanigamarājadhāniyo’ ti. "
327354,86,443,68,107,1,183,27,"Ko nu kho, bho gotama, hetu ko paccayo yenetarahi manussānaṃ khayo hoti, tanuttaṃ paññāyati, gāmāpi agāmā honti , nigamāpi anigamā honti, nagarāpi anagarā honti, janapadāpi ajanapadā hontī’’ ti?"
327355,86,444,2,12,1,80,7,"‘ ‘ Etarahi, brāhmaṇa, manussā adhammarāgarattā visamalobhābhibhūtā micchādhammaparetā. "
327356,86,444,13,35,1,143,15,"Te adhammarāgarattā visamalobhābhibhūtā micchādhammaparetā tiṇhāni satthāni gahetvā aññamaññaṃ[ aññamaññassa( sabbattha)] jīvitā voropenti, tena bahū manussā kālaṃ karonti. "
327357,86,444,36,68,1,181,24,"Ayampi kho , brāhmaṇa, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yenetarahi manussānaṃ khayo hoti, tanuttaṃ paññāyati, gāmāpi agāmā honti, nigamāpi anigamā honti, nagarāpi anagarā honti, janapadāpi ajanapadā honti."
327358,86,445,2,14,1,93,9,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, brāhmaṇa, etarahi manussā adhammarāgarattā visamalobhābhibhūtā micchādhammaparetā. "
327359,86,445,15,23,1,105,8,Tesaṃ adhammarāgarattānaṃ visamalobhābhibhūtānaṃ micchādhammaparetānaṃ devo na sammādhāraṃ anuppavecchati. 
327360,86,445,24,30,1,56,6,Tena dubbhikkhaṃ hoti dussassaṃ setaṭṭhikaṃ salākāvuttaṃ. 
327361,86,445,31,36,1,31,5,Tena bahū manussā kālaṃ karonti. 
