327369,86,449,2,22,1,59,7,58. Atha kho vacchagotto[ vacchaputto( ka.)] paribbājako yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami ; 
327370,86,449,23,28,1,39,4,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. 
327371,86,449,29,35,1,58,6,Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
327372,86,449,36,43,1,67,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho vacchagotto paribbājako bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
327373,86,449,44,55,1,44,7,"‘‘ sutaṃ metaṃ, bho gotama, samaṇo gotamo evamāha–"
327374,86,449,56,65,1,48,6,"‘ mayhameva dānaṃ dātabbaṃ , nāññesaṃ dānaṃ dātabbaṃ; "
327375,86,449,66,75,1,68,8,"mayhameva sāvakānaṃ dānaṃ dātabbaṃ, nāññesaṃ sāvakānaṃ dānaṃ dātabbaṃ; "
