327378,86,449,96,114,1,98,14,"Ye te, bho gotama, evamāhaṃsu‘ samaṇo gotamo evamāha mayhameva dānaṃ dātabbaṃ, nāññesaṃ dānaṃ dātabbaṃ. "
327379,86,449,115,124,1,68,8,"Mayhameva sāvakānaṃ dānaṃ dātabbaṃ, nāññesaṃ sāvakānaṃ dānaṃ dātabbaṃ. "
