327382,86,449,145,175,1,175,21,"Kacci te bhoto gotamassa vuttavādino ca bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ abhūtena abbhācikkhanti, dhammassa cānudhammaṃ byākaronti, na ca koci sahadhammiko vādānupāto[ vādānuvādo( ka.)] gārayhaṃ ṭhānaṃ āgacchati? "
