327421,86,473,2,4,1,13,2,8 . Tikaṇṇasuttaṃ 
327422,86,474,2,14,1,52,7,59. Atha kho tikaṇṇo brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
327423,86,474,15,34,1,136,16,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ… pe… ekamantaṃ nisinno kho tikaṇṇo brāhmaṇo bhagavato sammukhā tevijjānaṃ sudaṃ brāhmaṇānaṃ vaṇṇaṃ bhāsati–
327424,86,474,35,47,1,49,7,"‘‘ evampi tevijjā brāhmaṇā, itipi tevijjā brāhmaṇā’’ ti."
327425,86,475,2,17,1,68,10,"‘ ‘ Yathā kathaṃ pana, brāhmaṇa, brāhmaṇā brāhmaṇaṃ tevijjaṃ paññāpentī’’ ti?"
327426,86,475,18,60,1,300,30,"‘‘ Idha, bho gotama, brāhmaṇo ubhato sujāto hoti mātito ca pitito ca, saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā, akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena, ajjhāyako, mantadharo, tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ, padako, veyyākaraṇo, lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayoti. "
327427,86,475,61,73,1,51,8,"Evaṃ kho, bho gotama, brāhmaṇā tevijjaṃ paññāpentī’’ ti."
327428,86,476,2,24,1,107,16,"‘ ‘ Aññathā kho, brāhmaṇa, brāhmaṇā brāhmaṇaṃ tevijjaṃ paññapenti, aññathā ca pana ariyassa vinaye tevijjo hotī’’ ti."
327429,86,476,25,38,1,57,9,"‘‘ Yathā kathaṃ pana, bho gotama, ariyassa vinaye tevijjo hoti? "
327430,86,476,39,54,1,81,13,Sādhu me bhavaṃ gotamo tathā dhammaṃ desetu yathā ariyassa vinaye tevijjo hotī’’ ti.
327431,86,476,55,67,1,46,7,"‘‘ Tena hi, brāhmaṇa, suṇāhi, sādhukaṃ manasi karohi; "
327432,86,476,68,72,1,13,2,bhāsissāmī’’ ti.
327433,86,476,73,86,1,53,8,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bho’’ ti kho tikaṇṇo brāhmaṇo bhagavato paccassosi. "
327434,86,476,87,89,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
327435,86,477,2,23,1,144,17,"‘ ‘ Idha , brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi vivicca akusalehi dhammehi savitakkaṃ savicāraṃ vivekajaṃ pītisukhaṃ paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
327436,86,477,24,38,1,144,14,Vitakkavicārānaṃ vūpasamā ajjhattaṃ sampasādanaṃ cetaso ekodibhāvaṃ avitakkaṃ avicāraṃ samādhijaṃ pītisukhaṃ dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. 
327437,86,477,39,58,1,111,16,"Pītiyā ca virāgā upekkhako ca viharati sato ca sampajāno, sukhañca kāyena paṭisaṃvedeti yaṃ taṃ ariyā ācikkhanti–"
327438,86,477,59,69,1,67,8,‘ upekkhako satimā sukhavihārī’ ti tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. 
327439,86,477,70,87,1,156,15,"Sukhassa ca pahānā dukkhassa ca pahānā, pubbeva somanassadomanassānaṃ atthaṅgamā adukkhamasukhaṃ upekkhāsatipārisuddhiṃ catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati."
327440,86,478,2,19,1,154,16,‘ ‘ So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte pubbenivāsānussatiñāṇāya cittaṃ abhininnāmeti. 
327441,86,478,20,57,1,325,34,"So anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati, seyyathidaṃ– ekampi jātiṃ dvepi jātiyo tissopi jātiyo catassopi jātiyo pañcapi jātiyo dasapi jātiyo vīsampi jātiyo tiṃsampi jātiyo cattārīsampi jātiyo paññāsampi jātiyo jātisatampi jātisahassampi jātisatasahassampi, anekepi saṃvaṭṭakappe anekepi vivaṭṭakappe anekepi saṃvaṭṭavivaṭṭakappe–"
327442,86,478,58,72,1,122,12,"‘ amutrāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto amutra udapādiṃ. "
327443,86,478,73,87,1,122,12,"Tatrāpāsiṃ evaṃnāmo evaṃgotto evaṃvaṇṇo evamāhāro evaṃsukhadukkhappaṭisaṃvedī evamāyupariyanto, so tato cuto idhūpapanno’ ti. "
327444,86,478,88,94,1,58,6,Iti sākāraṃ sauddesaṃ anekavihitaṃ pubbenivāsaṃ anussarati. 
327445,86,478,95,100,1,36,5,Ayamassa paṭhamā vijjā adhigatā hoti; 
327446,86,478,101,106,1,27,4,"avijjā vihatā, vijjā uppannā; "
327447,86,478,107,118,1,78,10,"tamo vihato, āloko uppanno yathā taṃ appamattassa ātāpino pahitattassa viharato."
327448,86,479,2,21,1,155,17,‘ ‘ So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte sattānaṃ cutūpapātañāṇāya cittaṃ abhininnāmeti. 
327449,86,479,22,41,1,160,18,"So dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajānāti–"
327450,86,479,42,70,1,213,23,"‘ ime vata bhonto sattā kāyaduccaritena samannāgatā… pe… manoduccaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ upavādakā micchādiṭṭhikā micchādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā apāyaṃ duggatiṃ vinipātaṃ nirayaṃ upapannā. "
327451,86,479,71,102,1,228,25,"Ime vā pana bhonto sattā kāyasucaritena samannāgatā, vacīsucaritena samannāgatā, manosucaritena samannāgatā ariyānaṃ anupavādakā sammādiṭṭhikā sammādiṭṭhikammasamādānā, te kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapannā’ ti. "
327452,86,479,103,122,1,161,18,"Iti dibbena cakkhunā visuddhena atikkantamānusakena satte passati cavamāne upapajjamāne hīne paṇīte suvaṇṇe dubbaṇṇe, sugate duggate yathākammūpage satte pajānāti. "
327453,86,479,123,128,1,35,5,Ayamassa dutiyā vijjā adhigatā hoti; 
327454,86,479,129,134,1,27,4,"avijjā vihatā, vijjā uppannā; "
327455,86,479,135,146,1,78,10,"tamo vihato, āloko uppanno yathā taṃ appamattassa ātāpino pahitattassa viharato."
327456,86,480,2,20,1,150,17,‘ ‘ So evaṃ samāhite citte parisuddhe pariyodāte anaṅgaṇe vigatūpakkilese mudubhūte kammaniye ṭhite āneñjappatte āsavānaṃ khayañāṇāya cittaṃ abhininnāmeti. 
327457,86,480,21,54,1,184,22,"So‘ idaṃ dukkhan’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhasamudayo’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodho’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ dukkhanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti;"
327458,86,480,55,88,1,175,21,"‘ ime āsavā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ āsavasamudayo’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ āsavanirodho’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti,‘ ayaṃ āsavanirodhagāminī paṭipadā’ ti yathābhūtaṃ pajānāti. "
327459,86,480,89,105,1,117,14,"Tassa evaṃ jānato evaṃ passato kāmāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccati, bhavāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccati, avijjāsavāpi cittaṃ vimuccati; "
