327607,86,522,2,115,1,226,32,"‘ ‘ Tatra, bho gotama, yadidaṃ[ yamidaṃ( syā. kaṃ. pī.)] pāṭihāriyaṃ idhekacco anekavihitaṃ iddhividhaṃ paccanubhoti… pe… yāva brāhmalokāpi kāyena vasaṃ vatteti, idaṃ, bho gotama, pāṭihāriyaṃ yova[ yo ca( syā. kaṃ. pī. ka.)] naṃ karoti sova[ soca ca( syā. kaṃ pī. ka.)] naṃ paṭisaṃvedeti, yova[ yo ca( syā. kaṃ. pī. ka.)] naṃ karoti tasseva[ tassameva( sī. ka.), tassa ceva( syā. kaṃ. pī.)] taṃ hoti. "
