327787,86,561,93,94,1,7,1,Dutiyaṃ.
327788,86,562,2,4,1,16,2,3 . Venāgapurasuttaṃ 
327789,86,563,2,21,1,133,15,64. Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ yena venāgapuraṃ nāma kosalānaṃ brāhmaṇagāmo tadavasari. 
327790,86,563,22,26,1,43,4,Assosuṃ kho venāgapurikā brāhmaṇagahapatikā–
327791,86,563,27,41,1,76,9,"‘‘ samaṇo khalu , bho, gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito venāgapuraṃ anuppatto. "
327792,86,563,42,51,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
327793,86,563,52,97,1,142,15,‘ itipi so bhagavā arahaṃ sammāsambuddho vijjācaraṇasampanno sugato lokavidū anuttaro purisadammasārathi satthā devamanussānaṃ buddho bhagavā’ ti[ bhagavā( sī. syā kaṃ. pī.) idaṃ suttavaṇṇanāya aṭṭhakathāya saṃsandetabbaṃ pārā.1; dī. ni.1.255 passitabbaṃ]. 
327794,86,563,98,111,1,120,13,So imaṃ lokaṃ sadevakaṃ samārakaṃ sabrahmakaṃ sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiṃ pajaṃ sadevamanussaṃ sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā pavedeti. 
327795,86,563,112,125,1,135,12,"So dhammaṃ deseti ādikalyāṇaṃ majjhekalyāṇaṃ pariyosānakalyāṇaṃ sātthaṃ sabyañjanaṃ, kevalaparipuṇṇaṃ parisuddhaṃ brahmacariyaṃ pakāseti. "
327796,86,563,126,136,1,53,8,Sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’ ti. 
327797,86,564,2,9,1,70,7,Atha kho venāgapurikā brāhmaṇagahapatikā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
327798,86,564,10,48,1,322,32,"upasaṅkamitvā appekacce bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu, appekacce bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu, sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu, appekacce yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu, appekacce nāmagottaṃ sāvetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu, appekacce tuṇhībhūtā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. "
327799,86,564,49,57,1,77,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho venāgapuriko vacchagotto brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca–
327800,86,565,2,14,1,41,7,"‘ ‘ Acchariyaṃ , bho gotama, abbhutaṃ, bho gotama! "
327801,86,565,15,24,1,82,8,"Yāvañcidaṃ bhoto gotamassa vippasannāni indriyāni, parisuddho chavivaṇṇo pariyodāto. "
327802,86,565,25,42,1,71,8,"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, sāradaṃ badarapaṇḍuṃ[ maṇḍaṃ( ka.)] parisuddhaṃ hoti pariyodātaṃ; "
327803,86,565,43,53,1,80,8,evamevaṃ bhoto gotamassa vippasannāni indriyāni parisuddho chavivaṇṇo pariyodāto. 
327804,86,565,54,77,1,87,10,"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, tālapakkaṃ sampati bandhanā pamuttaṃ[ muttaṃ( sī. pī. ka.)] parisuddhaṃ hoti pariyodātaṃ; "
327805,86,565,78,86,1,80,8,evamevaṃ bhoto gotamassa vippasannāni indriyāni parisuddho chavivaṇṇo pariyodāto. 
327806,86,565,87,117,1,163,16,"Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nekkhaṃ[ nikkhaṃ-itipi( ma. ni.3.168)] jambonadaṃ dakkhakammāraputtasuparikammakataṃ ukkāmukhe sukusalasampahaṭṭhaṃ paṇḍukambale nikkhittaṃ bhāsate ca tapate ca virocati ca; "
327807,86,565,118,126,1,80,8,evamevaṃ bhoto gotamassa vippasannāni indriyāni parisuddho chavivaṇṇo pariyodāto. 
327808,86,565,127,176,1,383,35,"Yāni tāni, bho gotama, uccāsayanamahāsayanāni, seyyathidaṃ– āsandi pallaṅko gonako cittako paṭikā paṭalikā tūlikā vikatikā uddalomī ekantalomī kaṭṭissaṃ koseyyaṃ kuttakaṃ hatthattharaṃ assattharaṃ rathattharaṃ ajinappaveṇī kadalimigapavarapaccattharaṇaṃ[ kādalimigapavarapaccattharaṇaṃ( sī.)] sauttaracchadaṃ ubhatolohitakūpadhānaṃ, evarūpānaṃ nūna bhavaṃ gotamo uccāsayanamahāsayanānaṃ nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī’’ ti."
327809,86,566,2,35,1,295,28,"‘ ‘ Yāni kho pana tāni, brāhmaṇa, uccāsayanamahāsayanāni, seyyathidaṃ– āsandi pallaṅko gonako cittako paṭikā paṭalikā tūlikā vikatikā uddalomī ekantalomī kaṭṭissaṃ koseyyaṃ kuttakaṃ hatthattharaṃ assattharaṃ rathattharaṃ ajinappaveṇī kadalimigapavarapaccattharaṇaṃ sauttaracchadaṃ ubhatolohitakūpadhānaṃ. "
327810,86,566,36,63,1,55,8,"Dullabhāni tāni pabbajitānaṃ laddhā ca pana[ laddhāni ca( sī. syā. kaṃ.), laddhā ca( pī.)] na kappanti."
327811,86,567,2,18,1,100,11,"‘ ‘ Tīṇi kho, imāni, brāhmaṇa, uccāsayanamahāsayanāni, yesāhaṃ etarahi nikāmalābhī akicchalābhī akasiralābhī. "
327812,86,567,19,21,1,13,2,Katamāni tīṇi? 
327813,86,567,22,31,1,87,6,"Dibbaṃ uccāsayanamahāsayanaṃ, brahmaṃ uccāsayanamahāsayanaṃ, ariyaṃ uccāsayanamahāsayanaṃ. "
