327863,86,576,2,17,1,71,10,65. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate. 
327864,86,576,18,29,1,86,11,Tena kho pana samayena sarabho nāma paribbājako acirapakkanto hoti imasmā dhammavinayā. 
327865,86,576,30,45,1,39,6,So rājagahe parisati[ parisatiṃ( sī. pī.)] evaṃ vācaṃ bhāsati–
327866,86,576,46,53,1,44,5,‘‘ aññāto mayā samaṇānaṃ sakyaputtikānaṃ dhammo. 
