327923,86,587,2,4,1,15,2,5 . Kesamuttisuttaṃ 
327924,86,588,2,38,1,140,18,66. Evaṃ me sutaṃ– ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā kosalesu cārikaṃ caramāno mahatā bhikkhusaṅghena saddhiṃ yena kesamuttaṃ[ kesaputtaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] nāma kālāmānaṃ nigamo tadavasari. 
327925,86,588,39,43,1,30,4,Assosuṃ kho kesamuttiyā kālāmā–
327926,86,588,44,58,1,75,9,"‘‘ samaṇo khalu, bho, gotamo sakyaputto sakyakulā pabbajito kesamuttaṃ anuppatto. "
327927,86,588,59,68,1,65,9,Taṃ kho pana bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ evaṃ kalyāṇo kittisaddo abbhuggato–
327928,86,588,69,87,1,73,12,‘ itipi so bhagavā… pe… sādhu kho pana tathārūpānaṃ arahataṃ dassanaṃ hotī’’’ ti. 
327929,86,589,2,9,1,57,7,Atha kho kesamuttiyā kālāmā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; 
327930,86,589,10,47,1,322,32,"upasaṅkamitvā appekacce bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu, appekacce bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodiṃsu, sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu, appekacce yena bhagavā tenañjaliṃ paṇāmetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu, appekacce nāmagottaṃ sāvetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu, appekacce tuṇhībhūtā ekamantaṃ nisīdiṃsu. "
327931,86,589,48,56,1,66,8,Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te kesamuttiyā kālāmā bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ–
327932,86,590,2,12,1,53,7,"‘ ‘ Santi, bhante, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā kesamuttaṃ āgacchanti. "
327933,86,590,13,45,1,102,12,"Te sakaṃyeva vādaṃ dīpenti jotenti, parappavādaṃ pana khuṃsenti vambhenti paribhavanti omakkhiṃ[ opapakkhiṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.), omakkhikaṃ( ka.)] karonti. "
327934,86,590,46,56,1,55,6,"Aparepi, bhante, eke samaṇabrāhmaṇā kesamuttaṃ āgacchanti . "
327935,86,590,57,70,1,104,12,"Tepi sakaṃyeva vādaṃ dīpenti jotenti, parappavādaṃ pana khuṃsenti vambhenti paribhavanti omakkhiṃ karonti. "
327936,86,590,71,82,1,53,8,"Tesaṃ no, bhante , amhākaṃ hoteva kaṅkhā hoti vicikicchā–"
327937,86,590,83,99,1,66,11,"‘ ko su nāma imesaṃ bhavataṃ samaṇabrāhmaṇānaṃ saccaṃ āha, ko musā’’’ ti?"
327938,86,590,100,110,1,45,6,"‘‘ Alañhi vo, kālāmā, kaṅkhituṃ alaṃ vicikicchituṃ. "
327939,86,590,111,127,1,45,6,Kaṅkhanīyeva pana[ kaṅkhanīyeva ca pana( saṃyuttanikāye)] vo ṭhāne vicikicchā uppannā’’.
327940,86,591,2,41,1,192,26,"‘ ‘ Etha tumhe, kālāmā, mā anussavena, mā paramparāya, mā itikirāya, mā piṭakasampadānena, mā takkahetu, mā nayahetu, mā ākāraparivitakkena , mā diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā, mā bhabbarūpatāya, mā samaṇo no garūti. "
327941,86,591,42,49,1,37,5,"Yadā tumhe, kālāmā, attanāva jāneyyātha–"
327942,86,591,50,88,1,154,21,"‘ ime dhammā akusalā, ime dhammā sāvajjā, ime dhammā viññugarahitā, ime dhammā samattā samādinnā[ samādiṇṇā( ka.)] ahitāya dukkhāya saṃvattantī’’’ ti, atha tumhe, kālāmā, pajaheyyātha."
