328704,86,848,18,20,1,13,2,Katamāni tīṇi? 
328705,86,848,21,42,1,117,14,"Mūlagandho, sāragandho, pupphagandho– imāni kho, bhante, tīṇi gandhajātāni, yesaṃ anuvātaṃyeva gandho gacchati, no paṭivātaṃ. "
