328744,86,860,120,122,1,17,2,Bhagavā etadavoca–
328745,86,861,2,31,1,81,11,"‘ ‘ Yāvatā, ānanda, candimasūriyā[ candimasuriyā( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] pariharanti, disā bhanti virocanā, tāva sahassadhā loko. "
328746,86,861,32,103,1,447,40,"Tasmiṃ sahassadhā loke sahassaṃ[ tasmiṃ sahassaṃ( syā. kaṃ. pī.)] candānaṃ, sahassaṃ sūriyānaṃ, sahassaṃ sinerupabbatarājānaṃ, sahassaṃ jambudīpānaṃ, sahassaṃ aparagoyānānaṃ, sahassaṃ uttarakurūnaṃ, sahassaṃ pubbavidehānaṃ, cattāri mahāsamuddasahassāni, cattāri mahārājasahassāni, sahassaṃ cātumahārājikānaṃ, sahassaṃ tāvatiṃsānaṃ , sahassaṃ yāmānaṃ , sahassaṃ tusitānaṃ, sahassaṃ nimmānaratīnaṃ, sahassaṃ paranimmitavasavattīnaṃ, sahassaṃ brahmalokānaṃ– ayaṃ vuccatānanda, sahassī cūḷanikā lokadhātu."
328747,86,862,2,14,1,59,8,"‘ ‘ Yāvatānanda , sahassī cūḷanikā lokadhātu tāva sahassadhā loko. "
328748,86,862,15,21,1,49,5,"Ayaṃ vuccatānanda, dvisahassī majjhimikā lokadhātu."
328749,86,863,2,12,1,64,8,"‘ ‘ Yāvatānanda, dvisahassī majjhimikā lokadhātu tāva sahassadhā loko. "
328750,86,863,13,19,1,49,5,"Ayaṃ vuccatānanda, tisahassī mahāsahassī lokadhātu."
328751,86,864,2,36,1,103,11,"‘ ‘ Ākaṅkhamāno, ānanda, tathāgato tisahassimahāsahassilokadhātuṃ[ tisahassi mahāsahassiṃ lokadhātuṃ( syā. kaṃ.), tisahassīmahāsahassīlokadhātuṃ( pī.)] sarena viññāpeyya, yāvatā pana ākaṅkheyyā’’ ti."
328752,86,865,2,21,1,107,13,"‘ ‘ Yathā kathaṃ pana, bhante, bhagavā tisahassimahāsahassilokadhātuṃ sarena viññāpeyya, yāvatā pana ākaṅkheyyā’’ ti?"
328753,86,865,22,30,1,68,5,"‘‘ Idhānanda, tathāgato tisahassimahāsahassilokadhātuṃ obhāsena phareyya. "
328754,86,865,31,43,1,84,11,"Yadā te sattā taṃ ālokaṃ sañjāneyyuṃ, atha tathāgato ghosaṃ kareyya saddamanussāveyya. "
328755,86,865,44,60,1,100,11,"Evaṃ kho, ānanda, tathāgato tisahassimahāsahassilokadhātuṃ sarena viññāpeyya, yāvatā pana ākaṅkheyyā’’ ti. "
328756,86,866,2,32,1,34,5,"Evaṃ vutte āyasmā ānando( āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ)[( bhagavantaṃ)( sī.),() natthi syā. kaṃ. potthakesu. aṭṭhakathāya sameti] etadavoca–"
328757,86,866,33,51,1,81,12,"‘‘ lābhā vata me, suladdhaṃ vata me, yassa me satthā evaṃmahiddhiko evaṃmahānubhāvo’’ ti. "
328758,86,866,52,59,1,52,7,Evaṃ vutte āyasmā udāyī āyasmantaṃ ānandaṃ etadavoca–
328759,86,866,60,76,1,75,10,"‘‘ kiṃ tuyhettha, āvuso ānanda, yadi te satthā evaṃmahiddhiko evaṃmahānubhāvo’’ ti? "
328760,86,866,77,83,1,46,6,Evaṃ vutte bhagavā āyasmantaṃ udāyiṃ etadavoca–
328761,86,866,84,95,1,29,6,"‘‘ mā hevaṃ, udāyi, mā hevaṃ, udāyi. "
328762,86,866,96,118,1,156,17,"Sace, udāyi, ānando avītarāgo kālaṃ kareyya, tena cittappasādena sattakkhattuṃ devesu devarajjaṃ kāreyya, sattakkhattuṃ imasmiṃyeva jambudīpe mahārajjaṃ kāreyya. "
328763,86,866,119,131,1,55,8,"Api ca, udāyi, ānando diṭṭheva dhamme parinibbāyissatī’’ ti. "
