328779,86,876,2,18,1,70,8,"83.‘‘ Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, gadrabho gogaṇaṃ piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandho hoti–"
328780,86,876,19,60,1,28,5,"‘ ahampi dammo, ahampi dammo’ ti[ ahampi go amhā ahampi go amhāti( sī.), ahampi amhā ahampi amhāti( syā. kaṃ. pī.), ahampi go ahampi goti(?)]. "
328781,86,876,61,82,1,122,19,"Tassa na tādiso vaṇṇo hoti seyyathāpi gunnaṃ, na tādiso saro hoti seyyathāpi gunnaṃ, na tādisaṃ padaṃ hoti seyyathāpi gunnaṃ. "
