328784,86,877,2,17,1,88,11,"‘ ‘ Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, idhekacco bhikkhu bhikkhusaṅghaṃ piṭṭhito piṭṭhito anubandho hoti–"
328785,86,877,18,26,1,32,5,"‘ ahampi bhikkhu, ahampi bhikkhū’ ti. "
328786,86,877,27,54,1,232,25,"Tassa na tādiso chando hoti adhisīlasikkhāsamādāne seyyathāpi aññesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ, na tādiso chando hoti adhicittasikkhāsamādāne seyyathāpi aññesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ, na tādiso chando hoti adhipaññāsikkhāsamādāne seyyathāpi aññesaṃ bhikkhūnaṃ. "
