328794,86,880,2,16,1,58,6,"84.‘‘ Tīṇimāni, bhikkhave, kassakassa gahapatissa pubbe karaṇīyāni. "
328795,86,880,17,19,1,13,2,Katamāni tīṇi? 
328796,86,880,20,68,1,80,9,"Idha, bhikkhave, kassako gahapati paṭikacceva[ paṭigacceva( sī. pī.)] khettaṃ sukaṭṭhaṃ karoti sumatikataṃ[ sumattikataṃ( ka.), ettha matisaddo kaṭṭhakhettassa samīkaraṇasādhane dārubhaṇḍe vattatīti sakkataabhidhānesu āgataṃ. taṃ‘‘ matiyā suṭṭhu samīkatan’’ ti aṭṭhakathāya sameti]. "
328797,86,880,69,77,1,76,8,Paṭikacceva khettaṃ sukaṭṭhaṃ karitvā sumatikataṃ kālena bījāni patiṭṭhāpeti. 
328798,86,880,78,85,1,64,7,Kālena bījāni patiṭṭhāpetvā samayena udakaṃ abhinetipi apanetipi. 
