328823,86,887,2,4,1,12,2,5 . Sekkhasuttaṃ 
328824,86,888,2,13,1,52,7,86. Atha kho aññataro bhikkhu yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
328825,86,888,14,19,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
