328827,86,889,2,14,1,29,6,"‘ ‘‘ Sekho, sekho’ ti, bhante, vuccati. "
328828,86,889,15,26,1,37,7,"Kittāvatā nu kho, bhante, sekho hotī’’ ti?"
328829,86,889,27,37,1,44,6,"‘‘ Sikkhatīti kho, bhikkhu, tasmā sekhoti vuccati. "
328830,86,889,38,40,1,14,2,Kiñca sikkhati? 
328831,86,889,41,49,1,64,6,"Adhisīlampi sikkhati, adhicittampi sikkhati, adhipaññampi sikkhati. "
328832,86,889,50,61,1,47,7,"Sikkhatīti kho, bhikkhu, tasmā sekhoti vuccatī’’ ti."
328833,86,890,2,9,1,39,4,"‘ ‘ Sekhassa sikkhamānassa, ujumaggānusārino; "
328834,86,891,2,9,1,43,6,"Khayasmiṃ paṭhamaṃ ñāṇaṃ, tato aññā anantarā."
328835,86,892,2,25,1,40,7,"‘ ‘ Tato aññāvimuttassa[ aññāvimuttiyā( ka.)], ñāṇaṃ ve[ ñāṇañca( ka.)] hoti tādino; "
