328838,86,894,2,4,1,19,2,6 . Paṭhamasikkhāsuttaṃ 
328839,86,895,2,22,1,114,10,"87.‘‘ Sādhikamidaṃ , bhikkhave, diyaḍḍhasikkhāpadasataṃ anvaddhamāsaṃ uddesaṃ āgacchati, yattha attakāmā kulaputtā sikkhanti. "
328840,86,895,23,33,1,63,8,"Tisso imā, bhikkhave, sikkhā yatthetaṃ sabbaṃ samodhānaṃ gacchati. "
328841,86,895,34,36,1,12,2,Katamā tisso? 
328842,86,895,37,54,1,114,12,"Adhisīlasikkhā, adhicittasikkhā adhipaññāsikkhā– imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso sikkhā, yatthetaṃ sabbaṃ samodhānaṃ gacchati."
328843,86,896,2,19,1,93,13,"‘ ‘ Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti samādhismiṃ mattaso kārī paññāya mattaso kārī. "
328844,86,896,20,28,1,71,8,So yāni tāni khuddānukhuddakāni sikkhāpadāni tāni āpajjatipi vuṭṭhātipi. 
328845,86,896,29,32,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
328846,86,896,33,41,1,38,6,"Na hi mettha, bhikkhave, abhabbatā vuttā. "
328847,86,896,42,83,1,140,16,"Yāni ca kho tāni sikkhāpadāni ādibrahmacariyakāni brahmacariyasāruppāni, tattha dhuvasīlo[ dhuvasīlī( sī.) pu. pa.127-129( thokaṃ visadisaṃ)] ca hoti ṭhitasīlo[ ṭhitasīlī( sī.)] ca, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu. "
328848,86,896,84,94,1,88,9,So tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā sotāpanno hoti avinipātadhammo niyato sambodhiparāyaṇo.
328849,86,897,2,19,1,98,14,"‘ ‘ Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti samādhismiṃ mattaso kārī paññāya mattaso kārī. "
328850,86,897,20,28,1,71,8,So yāni tāni khuddānukhuddakāni sikkhāpadāni tāni āpajjatipi vuṭṭhātipi. 
328851,86,897,29,32,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
328852,86,897,33,41,1,38,6,"Na hi mettha, bhikkhave, abhabbatā vuttā. "
328853,86,897,42,59,1,140,16,"Yāni ca kho tāni sikkhāpadāni ādibrahmacariyakāni brahmacariyasāruppāni tattha dhuvasīlo ca hoti ṭhitasīlo ca, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu. "
328854,86,897,60,75,1,122,14,"So tiṇṇaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā rāgadosamohānaṃ tanuttā sakadāgāmī hoti, sakideva imaṃ lokaṃ āgantvā dukkhassantaṃ karoti."
328855,86,898,2,19,1,98,13,"‘ ‘ Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti samādhismiṃ paripūrakārī paññāya mattaso kārī. "
328856,86,898,20,28,1,71,8,So yāni tāni khuddānukhuddakāni sikkhāpadāni tāni āpajjatipi vuṭṭhātipi. 
328857,86,898,29,32,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
328858,86,898,33,41,1,38,6,"Na hi mettha, bhikkhave, abhabbatā vuttā. "
328859,86,898,42,59,1,140,16,"Yāni ca kho tāni sikkhāpadāni ādibrahmacariyakāni brahmacariyasāruppāni tattha dhuvasīlo ca hoti ṭhitasīlo ca, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu. "
328860,86,898,60,74,1,111,12,So pañcannaṃ orambhāgiyānaṃ saṃyojanānaṃ parikkhayā opapātiko hoti tattha parinibbāyī anāvattidhammo tasmā lokā.
328861,86,899,2,17,1,98,12,"‘ ‘ Idha pana, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlesu paripūrakārī hoti samādhismiṃ paripūrakārī paññāya paripūrakārī. "
328862,86,899,18,26,1,71,8,So yāni tāni khuddānukhuddakāni sikkhāpadāni tāni āpajjatipi vuṭṭhātipi. 
328863,86,899,27,30,1,14,3,Taṃ kissa hetu? 
328864,86,899,31,39,1,38,6,"Na hi mettha, bhikkhave, abhabbatā vuttā. "
328865,86,899,40,57,1,140,16,"Yāni ca kho tāni sikkhāpadāni ādibrahmacariyakāni brahmacariyasāruppāni tattha dhuvasīlo ca hoti ṭhitasīlo ca, samādāya sikkhati sikkhāpadesu. "
328866,86,899,58,71,1,116,13,So āsavānaṃ khayā anāsavaṃ cetovimuttiṃ paññāvimuttiṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja viharati.
328867,86,900,2,14,1,68,9,"‘ ‘ Iti kho, bhikkhave, padesaṃ padesakārī ārādheti paripūraṃ paripūrakārī. "
328868,86,900,15,32,1,51,6,"Avañjhāni tvevāhaṃ[ avañcuvanevāhaṃ( ka.)], bhikkhave, sikkhāpadāni vadāmī’’ ti. "
328869,86,900,33,34,1,8,1,Chaṭṭhaṃ.
328870,86,901,2,4,1,18,2,7 . Dutiyasikkhāsuttaṃ 
328871,86,902,2,21,1,114,10,"88.‘‘ Sādhikamidaṃ, bhikkhave, diyaḍḍhasikkhāpadasataṃ anvaddhamāsaṃ uddesaṃ āgacchati yattha attakāmā kulaputtā sikkhanti. "
