329039,86,948,11,30,1,148,14,"‘ tibbo no chando bhavissati adhisīlasikkhāsamādāne, tibbo chando bhavissati adhicittasikkhāsamādāne , tibbo chando bhavissati adhipaññāsikkhāsamādāne’ ti. "
