329059,86,954,65,82,1,87,13,"Yato kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlavā hoti, dussīlyañcassa pahīnaṃ hoti, tena ca vivitto hoti; "
329060,86,954,83,96,1,73,11,"sammādiṭṭhiko ca hoti, micchādiṭṭhi cassa pahīnā hoti, tāya ca vivitto hoti; "
329061,86,954,97,110,1,63,11,"khīṇāsavo ca hoti, āsavā cassa pahīnā honti, tehi ca vivitto hoti. "
329062,86,954,111,126,1,75,9,"Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave,‘ bhikkhu aggappatto sārappatto suddho sāre patiṭṭhito’’’."
329063,86,955,2,12,1,66,7,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, kassakassa gahapatissa sampannaṃ sālikkhettaṃ. "
329064,86,955,13,32,1,48,6,Tamenaṃ kassako gahapati sīghaṃ sīghaṃ[ sīghasīghaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] lavāpeyya. 
329065,86,955,33,39,1,51,6,Sīghaṃ sīghaṃ lavāpetvā sīghaṃ sīghaṃ saṅgharāpeyya. 
329066,86,955,40,57,1,53,6,Sīghaṃ sīghaṃ saṅgharāpetvā sīghaṃ sīghaṃ ubbahāpeyya [ ubbāhāpeyya( syā. kaṃ.)]. 
329067,86,955,58,65,1,56,7,Sīghaṃ sīghaṃ ubbahāpetvā sīghaṃ sīghaṃ puñjaṃ kārāpeyya. 
