329088,86,961,2,4,1,12,2,4 . Parisāsuttaṃ 
329089,86,962,2,15,1,26,4,"96.‘‘ Tisso imā, bhikkhave, parisā. "
329090,86,962,16,18,1,12,2,Katamā tisso? 
329091,86,962,19,27,1,43,6,"Aggavatī parisā, vaggā parisā, samaggā parisā."
329092,86,963,2,12,1,35,6,"‘ ‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, aggavatī parisā? "
329093,86,963,13,46,1,257,28,"Idha, bhikkhave, yassaṃ parisāyaṃ therā bhikkhū na bāhulikā honti na sāthalikā, okkamane nikkhittadhurā paviveke pubbaṅgamā, vīriyaṃ ārabhanti appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya, tesaṃ pacchimā janatā diṭṭhānugatiṃ āpajjati. "
329094,86,963,47,66,1,169,18,"Sāpi hoti na bāhulikā na sāthalikā okkamane nikkhittadhurā paviveke pubbaṅgamā, vīriyaṃ ārabhati appattassa pattiyā anadhigatassa adhigamāya asacchikatassa sacchikiriyāya. "
329095,86,963,67,74,1,38,5,"Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, aggavatī parisā."
329096,86,964,2,11,1,32,6,"‘ ‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, vaggā parisā? "
329097,86,964,12,34,1,155,17,"Idha, bhikkhave, yassaṃ parisāyaṃ bhikkhū bhaṇḍanajātā kalahajātā vivādāpannā aññamaññaṃ mukhasattīhi vitudantā viharanti, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, vaggā parisā."
329098,86,965,2,11,1,34,6,"‘ ‘ Katamā ca, bhikkhave, samaggā parisā? "
329099,86,965,12,35,1,170,18,"Idha, bhikkhave, yassaṃ parisāyaṃ bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, samaggā parisā."
329100,86,966,2,29,1,179,20,"‘ ‘ Yasmiṃ , bhikkhave, samaye bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, bahuṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū tasmiṃ samaye puññaṃ pasavanti. "
329101,86,966,30,43,1,88,10,"Brahmaṃ, bhikkhave, vihāraṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhū viharanti, yadidaṃ muditāya cetovimuttiyā. "
329102,86,966,44,60,1,109,12,"Pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ vediyati, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati."
329103,86,967,2,70,1,358,33,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, uparipabbate thullaphusitake deve vassante taṃ udakaṃ yathāninnaṃ pavattamānaṃ pabbatakandarapadarasākhā paripūreti, pabbatakandarapadarasākhā paripūrā kusobbhe[ kussumbhe( sī. pī.), kusumbhe( syā. kaṃ. ka.)] paripūrenti, kusobbhā paripūrā mahāsobbhe paripūrenti, mahāsobbhā paripūrā kunnadiyo paripūrenti, kunnadiyo paripūrā mahānadiyo paripūrenti, mahānadiyo paripūrā samuddaṃ[ samuddasāgare( ka.)] paripūrenti."
329104,86,968,2,31,1,192,22,"‘ ‘ Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, yasmiṃ samaye bhikkhū samaggā sammodamānā avivadamānā khīrodakībhūtā aññamaññaṃ piyacakkhūhi sampassantā viharanti, bahuṃ, bhikkhave, bhikkhū tasmiṃ samaye puññaṃ pasavanti. "
329105,86,968,32,45,1,88,10,"Brahmaṃ, bhikkhave, vihāraṃ tasmiṃ samaye bhikkhū viharanti, yadidaṃ muditāya cetovimuttiyā. "
329106,86,968,46,61,1,109,12,"Pamuditassa pīti jāyati, pītimanassa kāyo passambhati, passaddhakāyo sukhaṃ vediyati, sukhino cittaṃ samādhiyati. "
329107,86,968,62,72,1,33,6,"Imā kho, bhikkhave, tisso parisā’’ ti. "
329108,86,968,73,74,1,9,1,Catutthaṃ.
329109,86,969,2,4,1,20,2,5 . Paṭhamaājānīyasuttaṃ 
329110,86,970,2,45,1,116,14,"97.‘‘ Tīhi, bhikkhave, aṅgehi samannāgato rañño bhadro[ bhaddo( ka.)] assājānīyo rājāraho hoti rājabhoggo, rañño aṅganteva saṅkhyaṃ[ saṅkhaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] gacchati. "
