329229,86,995,35,68,1,95,15,"Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, api nu taṃ parittaṃ udakaṃ[ udakamallake udakaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] amunā loṇakapallena loṇaṃ assa apeyyan’’ ti?"
329230,86,995,69,76,1,11,2,"‘‘ Evaṃ, bhante’’."
