329287,86,1010,2,4,1,18,2,10 . Paṃsudhovakasuttaṃ 
329288,86,1011,2,32,1,74,7,"102.‘‘ Santi , bhikkhave, jātarūpassa oḷārikā upakkilesā paṃsuvālukā [ paṃsuvālikā( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] sakkharakaṭhalā. "
329289,86,1011,33,43,1,93,10,Tamenaṃ paṃsudhovako vā paṃsudhovakantevāsī vā doṇiyaṃ ākiritvā dhovati sandhovati niddhovati. 
329290,86,1011,44,71,1,105,10,"Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate santi jātarūpassa majjhimasahagatā upakkilesā sukhumasakkharā thūlavālukā[ thūlavālikā( sī. pī.), thullavālikā( syā. kaṃ.)]. "
329291,86,1011,72,80,1,76,8,Tamenaṃ paṃsudhovako vā paṃsudhovakantevāsī vā dhovati sandhovati niddhovati. 
329292,86,1011,81,91,1,102,10,Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate santi jātarūpassa sukhumasahagatā upakkilesā sukhumavālukā kāḷajallikā. 
329293,86,1011,92,100,1,76,8,Tamenaṃ paṃsudhovako vā paṃsudhovakantevāsī vā dhovati sandhovati niddhovati. 
329294,86,1011,101,114,1,65,6,Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate athāparaṃ suvaṇṇasikatāvasissanti[ suvaṇṇajātarūpakāvasissanti( ka.)]. 
329295,86,1011,115,127,1,104,11,Tamenaṃ suvaṇṇakāro vā suvaṇṇakārantevāsī vā jātarūpaṃ mūsāyaṃ pakkhipitvā dhamati sandhamati niddhamati . 
329296,86,1011,128,180,1,157,24,"Taṃ hoti jātarūpaṃ dhantaṃ sandhantaṃ[ adhantaṃ asandhantaṃ( syā. kaṃ.)] niddhantaṃ aniddhantakasāvaṃ[ aniddhantaṃ anihitaṃ aninnītakasāvaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)], na ceva mudu hoti na ca kammaniyaṃ, na ca pabhassaraṃ pabhaṅgu ca, na ca sammā upeti kammāya. "
329297,86,1011,181,197,1,109,14,"Hoti so, bhikkhave, samayo yaṃ suvaṇṇakāro vā suvaṇṇakārantevāsī vā taṃ jātarūpaṃ dhamati sandhamati niddhamati. "
329298,86,1011,198,234,1,140,18,"Taṃ hoti jātarūpaṃ dhantaṃ sandhantaṃ niddhantaṃ niddhantakasāvaṃ[ nihitaṃ ninnītakasāvaṃ( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)], mudu ca hoti kammaniyañca pabhassarañca, na ca pabhaṅgu, sammā upeti kammāya. "
329299,86,1011,235,279,1,102,12,"Yassā yassā ca pilandhanavikatiyā ākaṅkhati– yadi paṭṭikāya[ muddikāya( a. ni.5.23], yadi kuṇḍalāya, yadi gīveyyake[ gīveyyakena( ka.), gīveyyakāya(?)], yadi suvaṇṇamālāya– tañcassa atthaṃ anubhoti."
329300,86,1012,2,28,1,209,21,"‘ ‘ Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, santi adhicittamanuyuttassa bhikkhuno oḷārikā upakkilesā kāyaduccaritaṃ vacīduccaritaṃ manoduccaritaṃ, tamenaṃ sacetaso bhikkhu dabbajātiko pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti. "
329301,86,1012,29,51,1,224,21,"Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate santi adhicittamanuyuttassa bhikkhuno majjhimasahagatā upakkilesā kāmavitakko byāpādavitakko vihiṃsāvitakko, tamenaṃ sacetaso bhikkhu dabbajātiko pajahati vinodeti byantīkaroti anabhāvaṃ gameti. "
