329303,86,1012,77,90,1,64,6,Tasmiṃ pahīne tasmiṃ byantīkate athāparaṃ dhammavitakkāvasissati[ dhammavitakkovasissati( ka.)]. 
329304,86,1012,91,144,1,121,14,"So hoti samādhi na ceva santo na ca paṇīto nappaṭippassaddhaladdho na ekodibhāvādhigato sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato[ sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritavato( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.), sasaṅkhāraniggayhavārivāvato( ka.), sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāriyādhigato(?) a. ni.9.37; dī. ni.3.355] hoti. "
329305,86,1012,145,184,1,95,12,"So, bhikkhave, samayo yaṃ taṃ cittaṃ ajjhattaṃyeva santiṭṭhati sannisīdati ekodi hoti[ ekodibhāvaṃ gacchati( sī.), ekodibhāvo hoti( syā. kaṃ. ka.), ekodihoti( pī.)] samādhiyati. "
329306,86,1012,185,194,1,99,9,So hoti samādhi santo paṇīto paṭippassaddhiladdho ekodibhāvādhigato na sasaṅkhāraniggayhavāritagato. 
