329365,86,1031,2,4,1,21,2,1 . Pubbevasambodhasuttaṃ 
329366,86,1032,2,21,1,79,8,"104.‘‘ Pubbeva me, bhikkhave, sambodhā anabhisambuddhassa bodhisattasseva sato etadahosi–"
329367,86,1032,22,36,1,50,10,"‘ ko nu kho loke assādo, ko ādīnavo, kiṃ nissaraṇan’ ti? "
329368,86,1032,37,43,1,32,4,"Tassa mayhaṃ, bhikkhave, etadahosi–"
329369,86,1032,44,69,1,66,10,"‘ yaṃ kho lokaṃ[ loke( sī. syā. kaṃ. pī.)] paṭicca uppajjati sukhaṃ somanassaṃ, ayaṃ loke assādo. "
329370,86,1032,70,88,1,57,8,"Yaṃ loko[ loke( pī. ka.)] anicco dukkho vipariṇāmadhammo, ayaṃ loke ādīnavo. "
329371,86,1032,89,115,1,67,8,"Yo loke chandarāgavinayo chandarāgappahānaṃ, idaṃ loke nissaraṇan’ ti[ lokanissaraṇaṃ( aṭṭha.)‘‘ loke nissaraṇan’’ ti padena saṃsanditabbaṃ]. "
329372,86,1032,116,164,1,281,27,"Yāvakīvañcāhaṃ, bhikkhave, evaṃ lokassa assādañca assādato ādīnavañca ādīnavato nissaraṇañca nissaraṇato yathābhūtaṃ nābbhaññāsiṃ, neva tāvāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya‘ anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ ti[ abhisambuddho( sī. syā. kaṃ. ka.)] paccaññāsiṃ. "
329373,86,1032,165,220,1,276,28,"Yato ca khvāhaṃ[ kho ahaṃ( sī. pī.), khohaṃ( syā. kaṃ. ka.)], bhikkhave, evaṃ lokassa assādañca assādato ādīnavañca ādīnavato nissaraṇañca nissaraṇato yathābhūtaṃ abbhaññāsiṃ, athāhaṃ, bhikkhave, sadevake loke samārake sabrahmake sassamaṇabrāhmaṇiyā pajāya sadevamanussāya‘ anuttaraṃ sammāsambodhiṃ abhisambuddho’ ti paccaññāsiṃ. "
