329393,86,1036,2,44,1,71,10,"106.‘‘ No cedaṃ[ no cetaṃ( syā. kaṃ. pī. ka.) saṃ. ni.3.28 passitabbaṃ], bhikkhave, loke assādo abhavissa, nayidaṃ sattā loke sārajjeyyuṃ. "
329394,86,1036,45,59,1,68,11,"Yasmā ca kho, bhikkhave, atthi loke assādo, tasmā sattā loke sārajjanti. "
