329420,86,1043,2,4,1,15,2,7 . Arakkhitasuttaṃ 
329421,86,1044,2,14,1,58,7,110. Atha kho anāthapiṇḍiko gahapati yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; 
329422,86,1044,15,20,1,54,5,upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. 
329423,86,1044,21,28,1,65,7,Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho anāthapiṇḍikaṃ gahapatiṃ bhagavā etadavoca–
329424,86,1044,29,48,1,111,12,"‘‘ citte, gahapati, arakkhite kāyakammampi arakkhitaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi arakkhitaṃ hoti , manokammampi arakkhitaṃ hoti. "
329425,86,1044,49,64,1,164,13,"Tassa arakkhitakāyakammantassa arakkhitavacīkammantassa arakkhitamanokammantassa kāyakammampi avassutaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi avassutaṃ hoti, manokammampi avassutaṃ hoti. "
329426,86,1044,65,80,1,155,13,"Tassa avassutakāyakammantassa avassutavacīkammantassa avassutamanokammantassa kāyakammampi pūtikaṃ hoti, vacīkammampi pūtikaṃ hoti, manokammampi pūtikaṃ hoti. "
329427,86,1044,81,93,1,115,11,"Tassa pūtikāyakammantassa pūtivacīkammantassa pūtimanokammantassa na bhaddakaṃ maraṇaṃ hoti, na bhaddikā kālaṅkiriyā."
329428,86,1045,2,21,1,115,14,"‘ ‘ Seyyathāpi, gahapati, kūṭāgāre ducchanne kūṭampi arakkhitaṃ hoti, gopānasiyopi arakkhitā honti, bhittipi arakkhitā hoti; "
