329569,86,1079,2,22,1,133,15,"‘ ‘ Puna caparaṃ, bhikkhave, idhekacco puggalo sabbaso viññāṇañcāyatanaṃ samatikkamma‘ natthi kiñcī’ ti ākiñcaññāyatanaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
