329783,86,1125,48,81,1,91,9,So taṃ piṇḍapātaṃ gathito[ gadhito( syā. kaṃ. ka.)] mucchito ajjhosanno[ ajjhāpanno( sī. ka.) ajjhopanno( ṭīkā)] anādīnavadassāvī anissaraṇapañño paribhuñjati. 
